INSERT INTO `main_article` VALUES (38,'白宫《圣经》研读班的神秘主讲人是谁','2018-04-10 01:23:16.117757','2018-04-10 01:23:16.117792','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">美国现届的内阁为高层官员设立了一个《圣经》研读小组，这是百多年来的首次。他们在聚会时谈甚么？特朗普如何评价它？为什么女性不能在这个班授课？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这个小组每周的星期三都会在一个秘密地点碰头，在牧师带领下研读《圣经》的章节，每次聚会约60至90分钟。出于安保原因，负责官员保安工作的特勤局甚至拒绝向外界透露他们会面的确实地点。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这个高层的《圣经》研读小组主要为内阁成员而设，“赞助人”包括副总统彭斯、国务卿蓬培奥（Mike Pompeo）、能源部长里克·佩里（Rick Perry）和司法部长塞申斯（Jeff Sessions）等人。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他们都是大忙人，不能每星期都出席讲课，但只要有时间，他们都会尽量去。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">主持这些讲课的牧师德罗林格（Ralph Drollinger）认为，给政客讲课跟“政教分家”的原则没有冲突，因为虽然两者体制上分开，双方还是可以“互相影响”的。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-43645196\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中国网店下架《圣经》突然执法折射了什么</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/fooc-40104946\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">记者来鸿：宗教在俄罗斯为什么又吃香了？</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德罗林格今年63岁，住在美国加州，每星期都会坐飞机到首都华盛顿主持《圣经》研读课。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德罗林格的《圣经》讲课最初只会开放给众议员，后来这些议员获选为参议员，德罗林格便为这些参议员另开新班。到总统特朗普上任后，许多这些参议员进入内阁，德罗林格又为他们专门开设研读课。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他透露，前总统乔治布什在任时曾设立了一个性质差不多的《圣经》研读小组，但那是为低层官员设立的。他的研读班，是美国政府百多年来，首个专门给内阁高层官员举办的小组。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德罗林格每个星期都会把给内阁官员的讲课内容公开，给公众参阅。他上课时指，在上帝眼中，同性恋行为和同性恋仪式都是非法的，又指《圣经》支持资本主义制度内“私人财产”的概念。“《圣经》不支持共产主义。”他说。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但德罗林格同时指，这并不代表政客要跟随《圣经》的教义，把同性恋者处死。他认为，一些《圣经》旧约的规定是为古代以色列社会而设，不适用于现代社会，也不是教会的想法。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他忆述，曾有一名属民主党的基督徒议员向他求教：民主党支持同性恋婚姻合法化，这与她自己的看法完全不一样。他透露，他向这名议员解释《圣经》中的内容后，让她释怀了许多。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他指，这名议员现时仍不能公开谈论她的看法，因为如果她张口反对同性恋婚姻，选民很可能会离她而去。德罗林格补充，他不会要求她投票支持或反对任何议案，但她自己要考虑会否愿意出卖自己的信仰，让自己能继续留任，赚取议员的薪酬。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/13C1E/production/_100762908_hi045561055.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/13C1E/production/_100762908_hi045561055.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"美国能源部长佩里\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">EPA</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">美国能源部长佩里曾称赞德罗林格，形容德罗林格是他的&quot;生命导师&quot;。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德罗林格透露，自己小时候也曾经为信仰问题挣扎许久。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他小时候并不喜欢上教堂，也不喜欢阅读《圣经》，因为他不明白当中许多内容。直至他上高中的最后一年，有学校篮球队的拉拉队队长邀请他上《圣经》研读课。“我回家后，一个晚上把马修福音读了一遍。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他完成中学后，取得篮球队的奖学金进入大学。毕业后本来可以进入NBA成为职业篮球员，但最后选择加入美国宗教组织Athletes in Action的篮球队，到世界各地参加比赛，在中场休息时向观众宣扬基督教教义。他认为这对他来说是最好的安排，因为他“其实很不喜欢篮球，但对讲道更有兴趣”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他后来跟太太丹妮尔（Danielle Drollinger）在加州萨克拉门托市（Sacramento）开始每星期讲授《圣经》，最后他在华盛顿成立Capitol Ministries，把这种传道方式传至美国首都和43个州份的首府。德罗林格指，自己会把《圣经》中逐个篇章都解释一遍。他的讲学班可以花上一年去解释《圣经》中一卷书的内容。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这些小组分别都是由男性牧师领导，没有一名女性。德罗林格解释说，《圣经》里禁止由女性领导婚姻以及宗教组织，但这并不代表女性地位比男性低，这只是代表男女扮演不同的角色。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/6D4F/production/_100738972_gettyimages-841608592.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/6D4F/production/_100738972_gettyimages-841608592.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"特朗普去年签署法案前，曾带领多名高层官员一起祷告。\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">特朗普去年签署法案前，曾带领多名高层官员一起祷告。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他形容自己是“共和党中的保守派”，又指自己在共和党总统初选早期，已经开始支持特朗普。他透露，特朗普不是研读课的成员，但特朗普每星期都会收到课程笔记，也会给他回复，点评讲课的内容。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他指《圣经》中有教导政治与宗教要分家，但他不认为自己给政客讲课会破坏这个原则。他解释，体制上两者需要分开，但同时它们可以互相影响，因为家庭、商业公司、学校等等的社会组织都需要依靠上帝的话，才能“正确地运作”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他说，他不会教导听他讲课的政客如何投票，也不会游说他们要制定甚么政策。他说他只希望透过教导《圣经》里的章节，对方能自行决定。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他说，自己就像餐厅里的服务员一样，只是负责把上帝撰写的教义传达给听众。“我只是一个服务员，把厨师煮出来的食物从厨房传递到餐桌期间，我不会对它作任何改变。”</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-41829454\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">关于宗教改革500周年纪念的四件事</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2015/01/150111_debate_religion_freedom\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">BBC讨论：宗教信仰与言论自由</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那么，每星期三早上都给世上最有权力的人讲解《圣经》是一种怎样的感觉？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他说，他其中一个感觉在质问自己，凭甚么可以在这个位置给这些官员讲解《圣经》的内容？“上帝啊，我只是一个膝盖有点毛病的男人。为甚么你选择要我来干这种事？”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但他又回想，自己过去21年，都在向美国的公务人员传播上帝的话。“我想，从这个角度看，我还是世上最胜任这工作的人。”</p><p><br/></p>','美国现届的内阁为高层官员设立了一个《圣经》研读小组，这是百多年来的首次。他们在聚会时谈甚么？特朗普如何评价它','新闻',3,3,'article_img/20180410012316_79.jpg'),(39,'金正恩愿谈朝鲜半岛无核化 或要求美国就弃核赔偿','2018-04-10 01:26:27.777939','2018-04-10 01:26:27.777964','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">多家美国媒体引述不具名美国政府官员称，美朝双方正进行秘密接触，为历史性首脑会谈做准备，官员称朝鲜领导人金正恩愿意讨论半岛无核化问题，有关接触显示朝鲜对会晤的重视。这是华府官员首次证实双方就首脑会晤一事进行直接接触。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43374715\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">未就朝美会谈正式表态 金正恩在等什么</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43361226\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">特朗普与金正恩峰会筹备考验执行力</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">筹备谈判</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据报道，美国国务院官员透过驻联合国外交人员以及两国情报部门的秘密渠道，同朝鲜进行了初步沟通。朝美两国情报人员目前已经进行了多次接触，并已经在第三国见面商讨会谈地点。据称，朝鲜建议在平壤或蒙古乌兰巴托举行首脑会谈，但美国政府消息人士没有评论在何时何地举行会谈。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">朝鲜至今也没有就首脑会晤表态，此前美国主要依靠韩国去转达朝鲜对两国首脑会晤的想法。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">美国派出中情局长蓬佩奥（Mike Pompeo）以及局内一支团队，负责透过情报部门的幕后途径，筹备首脑峰会工作，蓬佩奥预料快将出任国务卿。蓬佩奥属于鹰派人物，曾扬言朝鲜可以改朝换代，由他主导谈判曾让外交界疑惑他对朝美首脑会谈有多大期待。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/722A/production/_100762292_hi045516827.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/722A/production/_100762292_hi045516827.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"蓬佩奥\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">REUTERS</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">蓬佩奥将主导美国在朝美谈判的工作。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另外，曾担任《华尔街日报》驻华记者的美国国家安全委员会亚洲事务官员博明（Matthew Pottinger）以及周一开始工作的国家安全顾问伯尔顿（John Bolton）都会在谈判筹备工作中有重大角色。伯尔顿同样是鹰派人物，他认为朝鲜问题正对美国构成“迫在眉睫的威胁”，对于那些认为美国有时间以外交途径解决问题的人，他嗤之以鼻，认为美国应先下手为强。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">朝鲜虽然表达了谈无核化的意愿，但双方会否对“无核化”定义有一致看法仍是未知数，也不清楚朝鲜会附带什么条件。朝鲜过往会要求美国撤军、并停止在日韩区设立核保护伞。日本《读卖新闻》引述消息称，朝鲜或要求美国保证朝鲜安全、并就弃核提供赔偿，朝鲜可以完全放弃核武。过去谈判中，朝鲜曾暂停导弹或核试，但谈判未果后，很快就会重新有所挑衅。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">韩国青瓦台消息人士形容，朝美接触进展顺利，不过韩方称不清楚两国交流到甚么程度。朝韩会谈将于4月27日举行；消息人士表示，正争取朝美会谈在5月底或6月初举行。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43575446\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">特朗普期待与金正恩会面，变数有多大</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43345487\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">特朗普与朝鲜会谈：三名赌客联手制造的牌局</a></p></li></ul><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/240A/production/_100762290_gettyimages-940811342.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/240A/production/_100762290_gettyimages-940811342.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"kim and k-pop\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">KCNA VIA KNS</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">韩星访朝鲜表演，与金正恩合照。</span></figcaption></figure></p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“纽约管道”</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">去年9月，当时还未被革除国务卿一职的蒂勒森（Rex Tillerson）公开承认，朝美双方有秘密直接沟通的渠道，不用透过韩国或者中国。有分析认为，这种外交方式就好像奥巴马政府当年处理伊朗、古巴问题般，透过连串秘密协商，争取达成协议。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">朝美双方秘密沟通渠道在官员间被称为“纽约管道”，也就是透过在纽约的驻联合国外交人员进行接触。“纽约管道”是自90年代初实行的方法，据《赫芬顿邮报》报道，当年克林顿上台后，朝美外交官在纽约斡旋下取得谈判进展，所以决定设立管道作沟通的方法。</p><p><figure class=\"media-with-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); white-space: normal;\"><p><img class=\"media-placeholder player-with-placeholder__image narrative-video-placeholder\" src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/720x405/p060mdpy.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px -25.6719px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; display: block; position: absolute;\"/></p><p></p><figure class=\"media-player\" data-playable=\"{&quot;settings&quot;:{&quot;counterName&quot;:&quot;zhongwensimp.world.story.43696503.page&quot;,&quot;edition&quot;:&quot;Asia&quot;,&quot;pageType&quot;:&quot;eav2&quot;,&quot;uniqueID&quot;:&quot;43696503&quot;,&quot;ui&quot;:{&quot;locale&quot;:{&quot;lang&quot;:&quot;zh-hans&quot;}},&quot;externalEmbedUrl&quot;:&quot;http:\\/\\/www.bbc.com\\/zhongwen\\/simp\\/world-43696503\\/embed&quot;,&quot;insideIframe&quot;:false,&quot;statsObject&quot;:{&quot;clipPID&quot;:&quot;p060mctq&quot;},&quot;playlistObject&quot;:{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Kim and Trump&quot;,&quot;holdingImageURL&quot;:&quot;https:\\/\\/ichef.bbci.co.uk\\/images\\/ic\\/$recipe\\/p060mdpy.jpg&quot;,&quot;guidance&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;embedRights&quot;:&quot;allowed&quot;,&quot;summary&quot;:&quot;Kim and Trump&quot;,&quot;liveRewind&quot;:false,&quot;simulcast&quot;:false,&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;vpid&quot;:&quot;p060mctw&quot;,&quot;live&quot;:false,&quot;duration&quot;:124,&quot;kind&quot;:&quot;programme&quot;}]}},&quot;otherSettings&quot;:{&quot;advertisingAllowed&quot;:true,&quot;continuousPlayCfg&quot;:{&quot;enabled&quot;:false},&quot;isAutoplayOnForAudience&quot;:false}}\" id=\"media-player-1\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 346.609px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 0px;\"><p><iframe id=\"smphtml5iframemedia-player-1\" name=\"smphtml5iframemedia-player-1\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"http://emp.bbc.com/emp/SMPj/2.18.15/iframe.html\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"\" gesture=\"media\" allow=\"autoplay\" title=\"Kim and Trump\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; width: 616.203px; height: 346.609px;\"></iframe></p></figure><p></p><figcaption class=\"media-with-caption__caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"border: 0px !important; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px !important; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\"></span>特朗普金正恩嘴仗全记录</figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">多年来，双方透过“纽约管道”断断续续进行过沟通对话。“纽约管道”有时亦成为谈判筹码，例如朝鲜不满美国对朝扩大制裁后，曾试过关闭通道，但有时美国亦会透过“纽约管道”争取释放被朝鲜关押的美国人。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">特朗普上台后，时任美国国务院朝鲜政策特别代表尹汝尚（Joseph Yun）有份重启“纽约管道”，他形容这是他的一项重大成就。尽管两国仍有争拗，但这条通道仍然在运作，尹汝尚是唯一一名与朝鲜官员有直接沟通的美国官员，他有份协助争取被朝鲜关押的美国大学生瓦姆比尔（Otto Warmbier），但这名大学生获释不久后便去世。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">尹汝尚在今年较早前因个人原因退休，当时惹来惴测这条管道会如何运作。据美国有线新闻网络，美国国务院亚太副助卿董云裳（Suan Thornton）以及专门处理朝鲜事务的副特别代表兰伯特（Mark Lambert）正透过“纽约管道”与朝鲜官员对话，商讨首脑会谈的准备工作。</p><p><br/></p>','多家美国媒体引述不具名美国政府官员称，美朝双方正进行秘密接触，为历史性首脑会谈做准备，官员称朝鲜领导人金正恩','新闻',1,3,'article_img/20180410012627_7.jpg'),(40,'日本建战后首支海军陆战队准备对付中国','2018-04-10 01:28:30.835417','2018-04-10 01:28:30.835442','<p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">昨天（4月7日）日本陆上自卫队下属的&quot;水陆机动团&quot;举行了成立仪式，这是在二战后海军陆战队首次出现在日本。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&quot;水陆机动团&quot;的约1,500军人在日本长崎县佐世保市的相浦基地参加了成立仪式。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">日本防卫副大臣山本朋广说，环绕日本安全局势日益严峻，&quot;离岛防卫&quot;至关重要。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-42503969\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">日本拟造新航母应对“来自中国的威胁”</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-39355064\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">应对中国日本添航母增加海军投送能力</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-39261336\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">背景：日本将赴南海的“准航母”有多大能力</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">日本新成立的海军陆战队约有2100人，包括水陆机动连队、水陆两栖战车部队、特科部队、侦察部队、设施部队、通信部队、后方支持部队、教育部队等单位。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">和平宪法</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">安倍晋三政府2013年根据长期国防政策指针《防卫计划大纲》制定的&quot;中期防&quot;（《日本中期防卫力量整备计划》）里面规定要建立&quot;机动师团和旅团&quot;及水陆两栖部队，以提高在日本西南诸岛方面的机动能力及岛屿防卫能力。</p><p></p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/5DB1/production/_100758932_973eafc8-64c0-4420-b2f9-118b0a7fe31f.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/5DB1/production/_100758932_973eafc8-64c0-4420-b2f9-118b0a7fe31f.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"japan navy\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">日本成立海军陆战队旅极具争议，因为两栖作战部队旨在对外投送兵力，在理论上能够对日本邻国构成威胁。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">日本成立海军陆战队极具争议，因为两栖作战部队旨在对外投送兵力，在理论上能够对日本邻国构成威胁。日本二战后在盟军占领下通过的&quot;和平宪法&quot;规定了 &quot;放弃发动战争的权利&quot;。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">1946年公布的日本&quot;和平宪法&quot;第九条规定禁止日本行使所谓&quot;集体自卫权&quot;，即军事同盟国遭受攻击时彼此提供军事援助的权利。日本宪法只允许日本受到攻击时行使个别自卫权。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">美国支持</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">美国多次要求日本行使&quot;集体自卫权&quot;，并且认为日本禁止行使集体自卫权会成为妨碍（美日）同盟关系的因素。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">不过2014年安倍内阁通过了&quot;解禁集体自卫权&quot;的重要修改，改变了战后70年来的&quot;专守防卫&quot;的基本国策。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">同年美国国防部长哈格尔对日本解禁集体自卫权表示&quot;欢迎&quot;，并表示&quot;日美需要建立牢固的关系，美国支持扩大自卫队的作用&quot;。</p><p></p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/14429/production/_100758928_60653cd9-7620-4fff-98e0-1c8ee6ad596d.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/14429/production/_100758928_60653cd9-7620-4fff-98e0-1c8ee6ad596d.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"太平洋战场上的&quot;塔拉瓦环礁战役&quot;\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">在1943年太平洋战场上日军在&quot;塔拉瓦环礁战役&quot;作最后抵抗，让美国海军陆战队付出沉重的伤亡代价。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">2014年美国总统奥巴马访问日本时表示明确支持安倍政权解禁集体自卫权，这是美国在任总统首次表态支持日本行使集体自卫权。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">二战历史</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">日本海军在上世纪20年代末开始成立&quot;海军特别陆战队&quot;。1932年1月28日晚，日军对上海闸北守军发动突袭，随后进攻江湾和吴淞。在进攻上海的战斗中日本投入了&quot;海军特别陆战队&quot;。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">在中日战争中和后来的太平洋战争中日本的&quot;海军特别陆战队&quot;被广泛使用。日军曾经在中国的大连和旅顺港都部署过&quot;海军特别陆战队&quot;。二战期间日本增加了&quot;海军特别陆战队&quot;的数量。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">在1943年太平洋战场上的&quot;塔拉瓦环礁战役&quot;中，佐世保第七海军特别陆战队的2619名官兵加上两千基地日军在塔拉瓦岛上面对美军两栖登陆进攻，拼死进行了3天抵抗，让美国海军陆战队付出了3千人伤亡的沉重代价。</p><div class=\"share share--lightweight  show ghost-column\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 32px 53.7656px 0px auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; overflow: hidden; zoom: 1;\"></div><p><br/></p>','昨天（4月7日）日本陆上自卫队下属的&quot;水陆机动团&quot;举行了成立仪式，这是在二战后海军陆战队','小说',3,3,'article_img/20180410012830_56.jpg'),(41,'中美贸易战酣之际南海刀光剑影风云激','2018-04-10 01:33:14.508774','2018-04-10 01:33:14.508803','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随着中美贸易战强硬言辞渐趋升级，双方都宣布派遣舰队前往南中国海。这轮经济摩擦会扩大为地缘斗争吗？南海的主权争议和航行自由问题是否又要升温？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国海军从4月5日开始了为期一周的&quot;实弹&quot;&quot;南海军事训练&quot;，其中包括航母&quot;辽宁舰&quot;的立体战斗群的40多艘战舰、潜艇、飞机。有评论人士认为，这是中国要显示其军事实力。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本周，美军&quot;罗斯福&quot;号航母打击群结束在中东地区的部署，进入<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-41499654\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">第七舰队辖区</a>，已经抵达新加坡。在中国举行这次演习之前，美国宣布将有 &quot;罗斯福&quot;、&quot;卡尔·文森&quot;和&quot;里根&quot;号三艘航母带领的战斗群同时部署在亚太地区。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3月22日，美国总统特朗普签署了针对中国多达600亿美元的进口产品加征关税备忘录；次日，美国海军&quot;马斯汀&quot;号驱逐舰便在南中国海海域进行&quot;航行自由&quot;行动，并进入南沙群岛美济礁12海里范围内。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国称派遣了两艘军舰对于美舰&quot;识别查证、警告驱离&quot;，中国国防部随后做出强硬声明称，美军此举是是&quot;对中方的严重政治和军事挑衅&quot;。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43519046\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">受中国压力 越南再次叫停南海石油项目</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43406210\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">赤瓜礁海战30年：一仗奠定南海格局</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43299835\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">卡尔文森号历史性访越跟中国有什么关系</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">除此外，3月5日，美国卡尔•文森号航母舰队访问了越南的岘港。&quot;罗斯福&quot;号去新加坡前和印度海军举行联合演习。加之其它亚太国家海军近期的演习，有评论人士认为这些举措也显示美越等国有在南海合围中国的政策。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中美两个大国的学者们都说，真正将<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43654210\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">贸易战</a>进行下去或者贸易战扩大为金融战、能源战甚至热战冲突，对两者来说都是两败俱伤，没有胜利者。但双方能避免掉进&quot;<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-42496533\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">修昔底德陷阱</a>&quot;吗？朝核问题刚刚随着朝鲜领导人<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43580809\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">金正恩访华有所降温</a>，什么热点和冲突又可能导向这一陷阱呢？</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">南海争议</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在宽阔的南中国海中，除了渔民以外，数千年的人类文明史上很少有人问津的大小岛屿在近两百年现代国家民族概念的冲击下，就南海诸多岛礁主权归属的国际争议开始，一直没有平息，从荷兰、法国、英国的航海探险家、殖民者到后来亚洲进入现代化发展、东南亚各国二战后陆续独立。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/9D5B/production/_100738204_l.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/9D5B/production/_100738204_l.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"2018年南海军演辽宁号航母\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">XINHUA NEWS AGENCY</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">2018年南海军演辽宁号航母首次“参战”。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随着<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-43301483\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">亚太</a>经济和贸易在世界上崛起，南海成为重要的国际能源和运输战略要道。其本身蕴藏的巨大能源、自然资源也不断提升这一过去人烟罕至地区的重要性。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">曾在越南工作过的英国记者比尔·海顿经过研究近日对BBC越南语部称，他个人认为中国对南海诸多岛屿主权声称是混乱和错误的，原因是中国官方首次声称对南海主权始于发现日本商人西泽吉次试图占据东沙岛。而对南沙群岛（the Spratly Islands ）的主权依据是&quot;（白眉初）个人所划的U形线，并非官方文件&quot;。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">海顿的这一研究似乎与中国官方和学者描述的历史不同：后者称中国早在清朝末期就曾与擅自闯入、占据南海一些岛屿的西方列强发生过外交纠纷，提出过抗议。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国学者称，在法国与上世纪30年代初占据南沙群岛9小岛事件后，1934年，中华民国&quot;水陆地图审查委员会&quot; 审定了中国南海各岛礁滩的中英文地名，次年出版了《中国南海岛屿图》，&quot;确定了中国南海最南的疆域线至北纬4°，把曾母暗沙标在疆域线之内&quot;。1936年中国北京师范大学历史地理部主任兼地理学教授白眉初据此划出的南海U形实线（即后来的11段线和9段线）成为后来中国的国境线提供了法理依据。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">实际占领</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2016年，海牙国际法庭就菲律宾请求建立的南海仲裁案仲裁庭做出仲裁，称在中国地图所绘的南海的九段线内，中国没有历史权利宣称主权。中国政府立即重申该裁决是无效的，中国拒绝接受承认。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">南海总面积是350万平方公里，包括中国所称的东沙、西沙、中沙和南沙，其中涉及主权争议的区域主要是南沙的部分。因为这一区域不仅自然资源丰富，更是处于世界经济的重心亚太经济的关键通道之上，因此备受国际关注。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/0212/production/_90303500_gettyimages-149332348.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/0212/production/_90303500_gettyimages-149332348.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"This aerial view of the city of Sansha on an island in the disputed Paracel chain, which China now considers part of Hainan province. File photo\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">近年来各国各方都加强其占领的南海岛礁建设。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">约半个多世纪以来，中国（包括<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/china/2016/11/161130_ana_taiwan_island_south_sea\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">台湾</a>）、菲律宾、越南等南海周边国家已经就南海一些岛礁和国界展开多年的外交争议。南海诸岛被各国军事占领，占领岛屿所在区域犬牙交错。中国和越南是占领岛屿最多的两方。双方为此甚至爆发过海战。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">近二十年来，在中国和东盟之间、中国和有关东盟国家之间的外交努力下，双方逐渐达成了一些解决分歧的外交共识，使得南海主权争议得到一定程度的化解，区域局势基本稳定。但有关国家和地区都没有停止对各自所占岛屿的强化建设。域外大国也表示对该海域未来航行自由的关注。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">今年3月份，台湾南沙太平岛海巡驻军进行 &quot;环岛海域实弹射击&quot;演习，还引起越南官方的抗议，认为其&quot;严重侵犯越南主权&quot;。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">崛起和重返</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">很多国际学者和专家们指出，<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/indepth/2016/07/160713_focusonchina_southchinaseaverdict\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">南海争议</a>的焦点并不在于一些无人居住的岛屿，或者是其周围有限的渔业资源或者深埋海底未开发的石油，实质是不断崛起的中国与传统上主导国际政治经济秩序的美国之间矛盾的一个反映点。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">南海仲裁结果公布前夕，中国全国人大外事委员会主任傅莹应邀在英国皇家国际事务研究所发表《失去与秩序再构建》的演讲，认为美国主导的世界秩序从没有完全接纳中国。而这种秩序已经无法适应世界发展客观需要，需要重建新的秩序。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">长期关注南海争议的新加坡国立大学东亚研究所所长郑永年在其《中国民族主义的复兴:民族国家向何处去》一书中认为，中国崛起必然构成对现行国际秩序的挑战，以西方民族主义的思路来理解中国民族主义，必然得出中国威胁论的结论，所以围堵中国成了美国为首的西方的自然选择。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他还表示，南海问题的恶化是美国&quot;重返亚太&quot;和中国对美国&quot;重返&quot;的反应两者之间互动的结果。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-42408674\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">南海争议岛礁：中国继续扩建军事设施引关注</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/fooc/2015/06/150624_fooc_south_china_sea\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">记者来鸿：中国到底打算在南海干什么？</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-39421950\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">美智库称中国接近完成南沙三人工岛工程</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;修昔底德陷阱&quot;</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网络媒体上对中美双方贸易冲突和在南海剑拔弩张的形势关注不少，有些甚至表示了对中美爆发<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43041099\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">军事</a>热战的担忧。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">仅从南海军事形势来看，中国国防大学教授金一南少将近日则对中国媒体表示，中国海军大规模演习在南沙群岛海域北部，而美军只有一个航母在这一海域南方，目前并不存在可能短兵相接、一触即发的危机。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从客观上看，美军的三个久经战火的航母群和中国一个训练性的航母群对比，凸现出目前<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-39202784\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美军事实力的差异</a>。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">目前，中美双方领导人在贸易战等问题上并未像很多网络媒体文章说得那样陷入你死我活的状态。特朗普在中国方面发动反击后干脆说，&quot;美国没有和中国进行贸易战&quot;。中国方面有关发言人也强调说：谈判的大门仍然敞开。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">作为中国加入世界贸易组织谈判的首席代表，龙永图接受中国媒体采访时就中美贸易战表示，“贸易本身就是一种交流、一种对话、一种谈判、一种妥协”。在这个问题上不慎重，“会使全世界感到<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-42755369\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中国的崛起就是对世界的威胁，特别是对美国的威胁</a>”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而金一南引述美前国务卿基辛格、美前国家安全顾问布热津斯基等曾就中美冲突发出的多次警告：如果中国被逼与俄罗斯真正形成结盟，将是西方地缘政治最大的灾难。</p><p><br/></p>','随着中美贸易战强硬言辞渐趋升级，双方都宣布派遣舰队前往南中国海。这轮经济摩擦会扩大为地缘斗争吗？南海的主权争','散文',1,3,'article_img/20180410013314_45.jpg'),(42,'扎克伯格：我才不会从脸书辞职','2018-04-10 01:36:15.934406','2018-04-10 01:36:15.934433','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">围绕脸书（Facebook）的风波还在发酵，脸书创始人马克·扎克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）周三召开电话记者会时坚称，他仍是领导公司的最佳人选。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">会上扎克伯格表示，在打造像脸书这种“史无前例”的事物时，“有些事情是你时会搞砸的”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“我认为人们应该要求我们负责的是，我们要从自己的错误中吸取教训。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">目前扎克伯格身兼脸书首席执行官与董事会主席职位。被问及公司是否有讨论他的职位变动时，他回答称：“据我所知没有！”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而在一个月前，可能没有几个人会提出这种问题。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但近期关于第三方不当收集数据、假新闻、舆论宣传等问题的报道使得外界开始质疑扎克伯格的领导能力，一些人认为脸书可能已经成长到一定程度，超过他控制范围了。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“根据架构，他不可能被解雇-他只能辞职”</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">纽约养老基金主管斯科特·斯特林格（Scott Stringer）表示，扎克伯格应于本周辞职。斯特林格主管的基金持有的脸书股票价值约10亿美元。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-42764202\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">脸书打假：优先推送用户认定的可靠新闻源</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-41425438\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">扎克伯格喊冤：凭什么都说我&quot;反特朗普&quot;？</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-42828323\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">索罗斯：谷歌和脸书给民主带来威胁</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">斯特林格向美国电视频道CNBC指出，脸书拥有20亿用户，但自己却处于未知的环境中，没能为用户提供满意的服务，也没能让用户感到自己的数据是安全的。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他呼吁扎克伯格下台，从而让脸书开启“提高声誉的第二篇章”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">财经记者费里克斯·萨尔蒙（Felix Salmon）日前撰文写道，“他（扎克伯格）领导的不仅仅是一个几乎可以接触到世界上所有人的机构”，“多亏了金融工程，他现在还拥有大股东投票权，并且控制着董事会，因此他可以不对任何人负责。根据架构，他不可能被解雇-他只能辞职。这正是他现在应该做的。”</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“一个经常被批评缺乏同理心的男人”</h2><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/436C/production/_100706271_mediaitem100706270.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/436C/production/_100706271_mediaitem100706270.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"A lit sign at Facebook HQ\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AFP/GETTY</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">扎克伯格说“删除脸书”运动影响有限。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">关于负面舆论和“删除脸书”运动带来的真正损失，扎克伯格的回答让我们了解到更多一点信息。目前为止他的回答是：不多。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他说，“据我们观察，目前并没有什么实质性影响”。随即他又补充道，“但你们看，这并不好！”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由于是电话记者会，我们并不能得知，在同一个房间里，扎克伯格的团队给他提供了多大程度的指导。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但对经常被批评缺乏同理心的扎克伯格来说，他在近一小时的记者会上表现得很强劲。记者会刚一结束，脸书的股价便上涨3%。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下周他可能会面临更严峻的情形，他将前往华盛顿在国会作证，这次他需要面对镜头。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这次记者会或许正是一场理想的彩排。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接下来几个月，随着以联邦贸易委员会（FTC）为首的机构对脸书调查逐步展开，以及对脸书如何操作公众数据的调查不断深入，围绕扎克伯格领导权的声音可能会发生戏剧性变化。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果脸书被认为未尽到应有责任，并被处以巨额罚款，那么该公司将会在人事调整上面临更大压力。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">截至目前，除作出道歉及承认判断不当外，扎克伯格还告诉记者，公司并没有因“剑桥分析”事件开除任何员工。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">责任在于他，他说。事实上可能也的确如此。</p><p><br/></p>','围绕脸书（Facebook）的风波还在发酵，脸书创始人马克·扎克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）周三召','小说',2,3,'article_img/20180410013615_92.jpg'),(43,'中美亮底牌后开始互动 特朗普：目前非贸易战','2018-04-10 01:39:31.849384','2018-04-10 01:39:31.849413','<p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 28px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">中美之间的贸易摩擦升级，美国宣布或向中国产品征税后，中国随即有所反击，同样计划向对方部分产品征收关税，不过中美双方均表示希望以谈判化解危机。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国总统特朗普表示，并不是与中国进行贸易战。白宫首席经济顾问库德洛（Larry Kudlow）认为中国会在贸易问题上让步，与美国达成协议。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">欧美股市暂时未有受到很大冲击，其中美股4月4日开市时低开，但在库德洛发表上述言论后，反弹以高1%收市。</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43595219\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-top-style: initial;border-right-style: initial;border-bottom-style: solid;border-left-style: initial;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220);border-left-color: initial;border-image: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3)\">中美贸易战会将中国推向“失落的二十年”？</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43553945\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-top-style: initial;border-right-style: initial;border-bottom-style: solid;border-left-style: initial;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220);border-left-color: initial;border-image: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3)\">中美战略性贸易摩擦：断定贸易战到来为时尚早</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-43531738\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-top-style: initial;border-right-style: initial;border-bottom-style: solid;border-left-style: initial;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220);border-left-color: initial;border-image: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3)\">中美贸易战：中国的余地和特朗普的目的</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43610276\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-top-style: initial;border-right-style: initial;border-bottom-style: solid;border-left-style: initial;border-top-color: initial;border-right-color: initial;border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220);border-left-color: initial;border-image: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3)\">中美贸易战阴影下的忧心者样本：美国红酒</a></p></li></ul><h2 style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(30, 30, 30);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1.5rem;font-weight: inherit;line-height: 1.5;margin: 32px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">会否谈判？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">北京早前已多次表明不想有贸易战，但也不怕真的打起来。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">中国驻美大使崔天凯与美国代理国务卿沙利文（John Sullivan）会面，历时约一小时，就经贸问题等交换意见。双方称有关会面是在华府宣布有关关税措施前已经安排。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">中方指，崔天凯重申了中美经贸问题上的立场，要求美方及早摒弃单边主义和贸易保护主义的做法，停止对华301调查，通过对话协商的方式同中方解决有关分歧。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">崔天凯对记者表示，中方依然倾向以谈判解决问题，但需要双方参与，会留意美国的做法。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;clear: both;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;display: block;position: relative\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/4D49/production/_100558791_gettyimages-936577972.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/4D49/production/_100558791_gettyimages-936577972.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"特朗普\" width=\"976\" height=\"800\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto;max-width: 100%;user-select: none;width: 616.203px;transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in;display: block\"/><span style=\"color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);overflow: hidden;border: 0px !important;padding: 0px !important;position: absolute !important;height: 1px !important;width: 1px !important\">图片版权</span><span style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(236, 236, 236);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 0.875rem;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: 0.25px;line-height: 1.14286;padding: 3px 8px 1px;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);bottom: 0px;position: absolute;right: 0px\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">路透社引述不具名美国经贸官员指，美国亦寻求以谈判解决与中方贸易的深层矛盾，但拒绝透露会否有更高级别的官员会晤。路透社分析，4月20-22日在华盛顿举行的国际货币基金及世界银行会议，可能是其中一个机会，让中美双方在场边讨论有关争议。</p><p><a class=\"off-screen jump-link\" href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhon