=\"section:subject\" style=\";padding: 0px;list-style: none;border: none\"><a class=\"TweetAuthor-avatar Identity-avatar u-linkBlend\" data-scribe=\"element:user_link\" href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump\" aria-label=\"Donald J. Trump (用户名: realDonaldTrump)\" style=\"background-color: transparent;outline: 0px;-webkit-box-flex: 0;flex: 0 0 auto;height: 36px;font-weight: inherit\"><img class=\"Avatar Avatar--edge\" data-scribe=\"element:avatar\" data-src-2x=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/874276197357596672/kUuht00m_bigger.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src-1x=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/874276197357596672/kUuht00m_normal.jpg\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/874276197357596672/kUuht00m_bigger.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;max-width: 100%;max-height: 100%;border-radius: 50%\"/></a><a class=\"TweetAuthor-link Identity u-linkBlend\" data-scribe=\"element:user_link\" href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump\" aria-label=\"Donald J. Trump (用户名: realDonaldTrump)\" style=\"background-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;-webkit-box-align: start;align-items: flex-start;font-weight: inherit\"><span style=\"display: flex;-webkit-box-align: center;align-items: center;min-width: 0px\"><span class=\"TweetAuthor-name Identity-name customisable-highlight\" title=\"Donald J. Trump\" data-scribe=\"element:name\" style=\"font-weight: 700;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;padding-right: 4px\">Donald J. Trump</span><span data-scribe=\"element:verified_badge\" style=\"position: static;-webkit-box-flex: 0;flex: 0 0 auto;padding-right: 4px\"><span style=\"position: absolute !important;overflow: hidden !important;width: 1px !important;height: 1px !important;padding: 0px !important;border: 0px !important;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px) !important\">✔</span></span></span><span class=\"TweetAuthor-screenName Identity-screenName\" title=\"@realDonaldTrump\" data-scribe=\"element:screen_name\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: rgb(105, 120, 130);font-size: 14px;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;flex-shrink: 1\">@realDonaldTrump</span></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577\" data-scribe=\"element:logo\" style=\"background-color: transparent;color: rgb(43, 123, 185);outline: 0px\"></a><p class=\"Tweet-text e-entry-title\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;list-style: none;border: none;white-space: pre-wrap;cursor: text;word-wrap: break-word;direction: ltr\">We are not in a trade war with China, that war was lost many years ago by the foolish, or incompetent, people who represented the U.S. Now we have a Trade Deficit of $500 Billion a year, with Intellectual Property Theft of another $300 Billion. We cannot let this continue!</p><a class=\"u-linkBlend u-url customisable-highlight long-permalink\" data-datetime=\"2018-04-04T11:22:03+0000\" data-scribe=\"element:full_timestamp\" href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577\" style=\"background-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-weight: inherit\">下午7:22 - 2018年4月4日</a><ul class=\"Tweet-actions Tweet-action--newsActions list-paddingleft-2\" data-scribe=\"component:actions\" role=\"menu\" aria-label=\"法推行动\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><a class=\"Tweet-action--heart TweetAction TweetAction--heartEdge\" title=\"赞\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/like?tweet_id=981492087328792577\" data-scribe=\"component:actions\" style=\"background-color: transparent;color: rgb(105, 120, 130);outline: 0px;display: flex;-webkit-box-align: center;align-items: center\"><span data-scribe=\"element:heart_count\" style=\"display: inline-block;font-size: 14px;vertical-align: text-bottom;margin-left: 3px;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;min-width: 0px\">14.2万</span></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"Tweet-action--replyEdge TweetAction TweetAction--replyEdge\" title=\"在 Twitter 上查看对话\" href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577\" data-scribe=\"component:news\" style=\"background-color: transparent;color: rgb(105, 120, 130);outline: 0px;display: flex;-webkit-box-align: center;align-items: center\"><span data-scribe=\"element:conversation_text\" style=\"display: inline-block;font-size: 14px;vertical-align: text-bottom;margin-left: 3px;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;min-width: 0px\">6.69万 人正在讨论这个</span></a></p></li></ul></blockquote><a href=\"https://support.twitter.com/articles/20175256\" class=\"Icon Icon--informationCircleWhite js-inViewportScribingTarget\" title=\"Twitter 广告信息与隐私\" style=\"background-color: transparent;color: rgb(43, 123, 185);outline: 0px;display: inline-block;height: 18px;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: contain;vertical-align: text-bottom;width: 18px\"><span style=\"position: absolute !important;overflow: hidden !important;width: 1px !important;height: 1px !important;padding: 0px !important;border: 0px !important;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px) !important\">Twitter 广告信息与隐私</span></a></twitterwidget></p><p id=\"jump-linkhttps://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/981492087328792577?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;ref_url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-43632315&amp;tfw_creator=BBCNews&amp;tfw_site=BBCNews\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1rem;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);overflow: hidden;border: 0px !important;padding: 0px !important;position: absolute !important;height: 1px !important;width: 1px !important\">结尾 Twitter 帖子 用户名 @realDonaldTrump</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国总统特朗普在推特（Twitter）表示，美国并不是与中国进行贸易战，只是不容许继续有贸易逆差及侵权的情况。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">白宫首席经济顾问库德洛（Larry Kudlow）认为，最终中国会退下来，与美国合作并达成协议。他的言论让美国股市由低开后反弹。</p><h2 style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(30, 30, 30);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1.5rem;font-weight: inherit;line-height: 1.5;margin: 32px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">甚么产品被征收关税？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">中国商务部发的公告表示，计划向106种美国产品进口商品征收25%关税，当中包括原产于美国的大豆、小麦、鲜冷肉类等农产品、部分汽车、烟草、威士忌、高粱产品、冷冻橙汁、化学品、部分飞机、塑料产品等。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">公告称：“涉及2017年中国自美国进口金额约500亿美元，最终措施及生效时间将另行公告。”</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17);clear: both;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;display: block;position: relative\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/7622/production/_100524203_34575.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/7622/production/_100524203_34575.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"美国犹他州詹森市的艾斯克兰迪农场正在收割燕麦。\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(189, 189, 189);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto;max-width: 100%;user-select: none;width: 616.203px;transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in;display: block\"/><span style=\"color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);overflow: hidden;border: 0px !important;padding: 0px !important;position: absolute !important;height: 1px !important;width: 1px !important\">图片版权</span><span style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(236, 236, 236);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 0.875rem;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: 0.25px;line-height: 1.14286;padding: 3px 8px 1px;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);bottom: 0px;position: absolute;right: 0px\">CNS</span></span><figcaption style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 16px;vertical-align: baseline;visibility: visible\"><span style=\"color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);overflow: hidden;border: 0px !important;padding: 0px !important;position: absolute !important;height: 1px !important;width: 1px !important\">Image caption</span><span style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(236, 236, 236);font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-size: 0.75rem;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: 1.33333;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;display: block\">美国犹他州詹森市的艾斯克兰迪农场正在收割燕麦。评论认为，中国如果采取贸易反制措施，将使美国农业遭受严重打击。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">而中国声明中，针对的飞机为“空载重量超过15000公斤，但不超过45000公斤的飞机及其他航空器”，中国媒体进一步说明，这是涉及波音737系列和737 MAX 7，没有提及波音较新、利润较大的的737 MAX 8、9、10系列。不过中国提出的措施已令波音股价受压。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国则宣称拟向中国1300种中国产品征收25%关税，涉及的层面十分广泛，由焗炉、电视等家庭用品、半导体、通讯卫星、火箭发射台科技产品、医疗器械、药物疫苗、工业机器等等。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美方指责中国窃取知识产权，强迫美国公司与中国企业分享技术，认为目前拟定的关税已考虑到潜在对美国经济的损害，并相信能争取中国撤销其有害的行为、政策与措施。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">最终产品清单预料经过公众咨询和审视，约两个月后实行。</p><h2 style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(30, 30, 30);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1.5rem;font-weight: inherit;line-height: 1.5;margin: 32px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">真的会爆发贸易战？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国数字显示，美国去年与中国的货品及服务交易，超过7000亿美元。双方今次拟定的关税措施所针对的产品，均是估计每年约500亿美元的交易额。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国商务部长威尔伯‧罗斯（Wilbur Ross）表示，中国针对的这批产品，只是占美国国民生产总值（GDP）的0.3% ，并不认为这会危害到美国经济。</p><p><figure class=\"media-portrait no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;clear: both;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;display: block;position: relative\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/11B04/production/_100525427_us_china_trade_import_export_ws_chinese-nc.png\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/11B04/production/_100525427_us_china_trade_import_export_ws_chinese-nc.png\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"GRAPH\" width=\"640\" height=\"695\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px;color: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;letter-spacing: inherit;line-height: inherit;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto;max-width: 100%;user-select: none;width: 616.203px;transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in;display: block\"/></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国经济专家认为，相关措施目前规模尚未大到会撼动整体经济，但警告如果摩擦加剧会对商业活动构成更大风险。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">标准普尔分析认为，中国近年减少了对出口的依赖，这可以帮助减轻美国加征关税带来的影响。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2016年，中国整体出口货品中，有18.2%是出口至美国。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">不过，标普高级经济师潘戴（Satyam Panday）表示，这种以牙还牙式的不稳定性动摇商界信心。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">“为甚么我会在未有把握的时候投资呢？”他说。</p><p style=\"border: 0px;color: rgb(64, 64, 64);font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.75;margin-top: 18px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">美国商界组织呼吁两国尝试对话解决问题，忧虑这种威胁性的关税措施会演变成危害美国经济的冲突。</p><p><br/></p>','中美之间的贸易摩擦升级，美国宣布或向中国产品征税后，中国随即有所反击，同样计划向对方部分产品征收关税，不过中','小说',5,3,'article_img/20180410013931_32.jpg'),(44,'德国高速公路不限速 何以事故率不高','2018-04-10 01:40:14.581736','2018-04-10 01:40:14.581761','<p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">世界最早的封闭高速公路系统诞生于德国，但是现在世界上规模最大的高速公路系统在中国。德国高速公路以没有限速而闻名。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">截至2016年底，中国大陆高速公路的通车总里程突破13万公里（超过了美国），是世界上规模最大的高速公路系统。2016年，德国高速公路网的总长度为12,996公里，考虑到德国面积只相当于中国的1/30，因此德国是世界上高速公路最稠密和最长的国家之一。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2008/11/081127_motorway_50yrs.shtml\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">英国高速公路50年</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2007/06/070625_roadsafety.shtml\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">英国最危险公路在哪里？</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然德国高速公路没有法定限速，但根据每10万人为单位统计的交通事故死亡率，德国的交通死亡率为6.8，远低于美国的12.9。而中国以10万人为统计单位的交通死亡率高达18.8，不仅高于中等收入国家18.5的水平，而且达到高收入国家9.3比例的两倍。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">平均时速142公里</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英国《独立报》记者布朗把德国的高速公路同美国做了比较，他认为德国高速公路是世界上驾车旅行最好的高速公路系统之一，同美国公路相比，德国公路上的靓车更多。他认为德国高速公路没有限速，高速公路上很少看到警察/警车也是德国系统优越的方面。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">准确地说，德国高速公路对一些车辆并没有联邦规定的限速，但是在城市，和标准低的公路，事故多发段和施工地区仍然有临时或常设的限速规定。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据2008年的一个统计，德国高速公路网52%的路段只有建议的最高速度，没有法定限速。15%的路段因为天气和交通情况有临时限速，33%的路段有常设限速规定。2006年德国对6车道高速公路的测量显示，在正常状态下德国高速公路上的平均车速为每小时142公里。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国高速公路一般都由多层水泥筑成，更适合高速行驶的需要。德国高速公路的路面经常定期经过检测，查看有无不规整或损毁。如果发现了上述情况，整个受影响的路面会被更换。许多美国人认为德国路面质量和公路养护优于美国。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然没有法定限速，但德国高速公路的建议最高速度为每小时130公里，虽然超过此限并不违法，但发生交通事故时，超速驾车者要承担更大的事故责任。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在德国汽车保险公司一般的政策是，当汽车在每小时200公里速度行驶时发生车祸，即使在高速驾车者并无其他过错的情况下，保险公司的赔偿支付会大大减少，甚至完全不予赔偿。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/D5FA/production/_100687745_c29b7763-a923-4564-bb1e-e17a35a261d5.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/D5FA/production/_100687745_c29b7763-a923-4564-bb1e-e17a35a261d5.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"beijing\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">截至2016年底，中国大陆高速公路的通车总里程突破13万公里（超过了美国）是世界上规模最大的高速公路系统。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当然现在德国高速公路不限速的路段在减少，一些德国人认为高速公路不限速是德国的弊端，他们责怪德国立法议员不作为，没有规定高速公路限速。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">交规和驾考更严格</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《独立报》把德国公路系统优于美国的原因总结为8个，除了不限速，德国驾车者更遵守交通规则。德国公路和美国大部分公路一样，超车在左边车道进行，右边车道正常行驶。在不超车的情况下，必须靠右行驶。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《独立报》认为，和美国的主要不同是，德国驾车者都严格遵守以上规则，而美国人则很少遵守。因为德国人更尊重这种规定，高速公路交通就能更顺畅。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英国读者认为，美国人不太受车道约束，美国许多州允许从左或从右超车。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国汽车严格执行定期检查。定期检车有助于减少潜在危险车辆的数目，减少对驾车者和其他车辆的威胁。《独立报》说，美国一些州的车辆检查同德国的相比就像是开玩笑。德国全国保持统一标准，而美国的车检各州都不一样。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国驾车水平整体高于美国，是因为德国有更严格的驾照考试系统。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在德国考取驾照，报考者需要上很多驾驶课程，包括在实际高速公路上的驾驶课，体验真实的高速交通。另外驾车者要接受基本的急救训练，另外还要经过难度很高的多项选择笔试和路考。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果一切顺利，完成这个过程需要6个月事件，考试者要付出2000美元的代价。显然在德国驾车，需要有更多的决心和投入。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国公路交通倍受赞扬的另外一个原因是行车距离保持得比较好。《独立报》文章说，虽然在德国公路上警察不多，但是如果你没有和前面保持足够车距，就会受到严厉的罚款，罚款可高达450美元。在美国如果发生同样的情况，州警察如果眨一下眼睛就算不错了。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国公路上的警察比美国少也被认为是德国公路系统的优点。《独立报》文章作者认为，警察会令一些驾车者感到紧张，即使他们没有做违法的事情。而在德国高速公路上，驾车者就很少会因为看到警察而紧张。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另外一个优点是，德国道路系统免费行驶，没有收费站。目前德国唯一要付费的车辆是货车。一般驾车者不需要停车付费，但是这样也就减少了路途停车的次数。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/60CA/production/_100687742_ba3ef6af-9027-4435-8967-978f6da0d5df.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/60CA/production/_100687742_ba3ef6af-9027-4435-8967-978f6da0d5df.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"1930s autobahn\" width=\"766\" height=\"511\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">纳粹德国时期德国新修的高速公路被称为&quot;希特勒的公路&quot;，在纳粹宣传中被称为全民就业的典范工程。</span></figcaption></figure></p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高速公路始于德国</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国是世界上最早建设封闭高速公路系统的国家。1932年德国第一条高速公路在科隆和波恩之间修建完成，当时的科隆市长（未来的西德总理）阿登纳主持了高速公路开幕典礼。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">早在1920年代中期魏玛共和国就有建设专门供汽车使用的高速公路的计划，但因为缺乏经济支持和政治共识，高速公路项目在纳粹上台以前主要停留在计划阶段。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国航空界出于担心来自汽车交通的竞争，极力反对建立封闭的高速公路系统，连德国汽车协会对耗资巨大的高速公路也不热心。1933年希特勒上台后才改变了这个局面，因为希特勒认为铁路运输已经过时，公路运输是未来。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当时德国新修的高速公路被称为“希特勒的公路”，在纳粹宣传中被称为全民就业的典范工程。这实际上是德国工程师弗利兹·托特力主通过修建高速公路系统，振兴德国经济。他的主张被纳粹政权采纳，他本人也被任命为“德国公路系统总监”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">德国最初修建的高速公路并没有像现在高速公路中间那样显著的隔离装置。按照许多高速公路设计，在战争中把德国高速公路的间隔离填平可以用做飞机跑道。但在二战期间由于盟军轰炸对德国公路系统的破坏以及德国飞机产量不足，这个设计考虑基本没有成为现实。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">历史学者认为，纳粹德国高速公路的军事目的往往被夸大。二战期间德军运输并不依赖于高速公路，特别是战争后期由于燃料缺乏，德军越来越多依靠骡马而非汽车。反而是盟军开进德国后大量使用高速公路系统。</p><p><br/></p>','世界最早的封闭高速公路系统诞生于德国，但是现在世界上规模最大的高速公路系统在中国。德国高速公路以没有限速而闻','小说',1,3,'article_img/20180410014014_17.jpg'),(45,'陈香梅去世： 曾游刃于中美台之间的飞虎将军夫人','2018-04-10 01:42:16.871624','2018-04-10 01:42:16.871651','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据《华盛顿邮报》报道，飞虎队将军陈纳德（Claire Lee Chennault）遗孀陈香梅3月30日在华盛顿家中过世，享年94岁。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">女儿陈美丽称，陈香梅因去年12月中风后出现的并发症而过世。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">二战期间，陈香梅与在中国支援抗日的飞虎队指挥官陈纳德将军结识并于1947年结婚，后移居美国。1958年陈纳德去世后，陈香梅逐渐步入政坛，在美国共和党中担任要职，并担任过八届共和党政府的顾问。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1981年，陈香梅作为当选总统里根的特使访问中国，受到中国领导人邓小平的招待。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/china/2015/07/150704_taiwan_military_display_wwii\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">台湾纪念抗战胜利70周年军力展示登场</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/china/2014/07/140707_ana_wwii_china_japan\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">分析：被湮没在历史教科书中的抗战历史</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">战乱中的爱情</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“他进入我的生命中，像春日的和风吹醒了百花，像四月的阵雨润泽了大地。”陈香梅在回忆录中深情地回忆自己与丈夫陈纳德的相遇。这次相遇发生在1944年的昆明。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">彼时，19岁的陈香梅刚从岭南大学毕业，成为中央通讯社记者。她被派往昆明分社，采访战功赫赫的“飞虎队”将军陈纳德。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/5685/production/_100694122_gettyimages-80272748.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/5685/production/_100694122_gettyimages-80272748.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"。\" width=\"2048\" height=\"2048\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">”飞虎队“老兵展示陈纳德的照片</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">陈纳德来中国之前，日军正在对中国后方城市进行狂轰滥炸，陪都重庆受损尤其严重，半壁山城已被炸毁，而中国空军实力薄弱，几乎没有还手之力。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1940年，刚刚退役的美国空军上尉陈纳德，受蒋介石和宋美龄邀请，赴华组建美国志愿航空队。在他的斡旋下，美国政府同意预备役和退役军官参加航空队。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">陈纳德在美国招募了112名飞行员和机械师，国民政府随即委任这批人马组成中国空军美国志愿航空队，由陈纳德担任指挥官兼大队长，总部就设在昆明。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第一次见到陈纳德，陈香梅回忆，“他脸孔布满深刻的皱纹，有着一个倔强的下颚，看起来强忍而果决，一堆深沉的棕色眸子却流露着坚忍的深色。”在随后的几次采访中，两人的关系越来越近。相识后第二年，抗战结束。陈纳德回到美国迅速与当时的妻子办理离婚手续，然后启程返回中国，抵达的第一天就向陈香梅求婚。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是两人的年龄差了三十岁，婚事遭到陈香梅父亲的反对，最终抵不过女儿的坚持，还是同意了婚事。两人这才在上海举行婚礼。</p><p><figure class=\"media-portrait has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/A4A5/production/_100694124_1172570-cns.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/A4A5/production/_100694124_1172570-cns.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"2016年，陈香梅在纽约出席91岁寿辰图片展\" width=\"2209\" height=\"3314\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">CNS</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">2016年，陈香梅在纽约出席91岁寿辰图片展</span></figcaption></figure></p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">美国政坛的华人面孔</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">婚后，夫妇两人迁居美国生活，养育了两个女儿，陈美华和陈美丽，两个女儿的名字是在台湾时宋美龄所取，也被宋美龄认作干女儿。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这期间，陈香梅还协助陈纳德将军完成了回忆录《一个斗士的自述》，但好景不长，1956年，陈纳德被查出患有肺癌，手术后也并未好转。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1958年，时任美国总统艾森豪威尔将陈纳德晋升为中将，几个月后，他就病重逝世。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">陈香梅也迎来人生较为艰难的一段，她陷入了和陈纳德和前妻所生子女的财产纠纷中。生活所迫，年仅33岁陈香梅把家搬到了华盛顿，独自扶养两个女儿。她找了份翻译的工作，并开始进行写书、巡回演讲。她先后出版数十部中英文作品，其中回忆录《一千个春天》被《纽约时报》列为全美十大畅销书之一。此后，她还涉足商界，成为飞虎航空公司副总裁。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于在美国最初的时光，陈香梅在给蒋经国夫人蒋方良的一封信中说，“我初来美国时年纪轻，我的丈夫虽然爱我，但他是美国人，无论如何无法了解一个中国少女异乡异客的心情，虽然我曾随着陈纳德将军领略了很多民众对英雄的崇拜与喝彩，但我总觉得自己只是一个影子，阳光西落时，影子也不知飘落何处。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">陈香梅不甘于做“影子”，她开始在美国政坛崭露头角。1963年，陈香梅初涉政坛，接受时任总统肯尼迪委任，成为第一位进入白宫工作的华人，此后，先后被八位总统委以重任，为尼克松、里根等政府工作。1989年，在老布什政府，她再次担任总统核心顾问职位。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">陈香梅成为了华盛顿政治圈最有影响力的华人女性。有外界评论称，她在冷战的特殊时期，成为中美沟通的“掮客”，只担任有职无薪的顾问角色。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">成功斡旋于中美台</h2><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/F2C5/production/_100694126_671720-cns.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/F2C5/production/_100694126_671720-cns.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"。\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">CNS</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">习近平向陈香梅颁发中国人民抗日战争胜利70周年纪念章</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1981年，陈香梅回到自己的出生地北京，但有了新身份：美国总统里根特使。这次出访，是陈香梅阔别33年后首次回到中国。时任中国领导人邓小平与代表团会面，将陈香梅放到接待主座，并说“陈香梅坐第一，参议员史蒂文斯先生坐第二，因为参议员在美国有100个，而陈香梅嘛，不要说美国，就是全世界也只有一个。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">陈香梅刚离开北京，就转道台湾，会见政要。在台湾期间，她称自己“不做信差，亦不代人传话”，但蒋介石、蒋经国、李登辉，甚至陈水扁都与她保持联系，使外界加深了她两岸密使的身份。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这种猜测并非没有根据。陈香梅不仅是陈纳德妻子，当时中国负责侨务的廖承志还是她的堂舅父，而陈香梅又与蒋介石、宋美龄私交甚笃，再加上她在华盛顿的影响力，因此具有沟通“中、美、台”三地的人脉和能力。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">冷战结束后，陈香梅的主要精力都放在中美交流事务，曾多次率领美国企业代表来华投资、交流。2015年，中国国家主席习近平向陈香梅颁发抗战胜利70周年纪念章。</p><p><br/></p>','据《华盛顿邮报》报道，飞虎队将军陈纳德（Claire Lee Chennault）遗孀陈香梅3月30日在华盛','散文',2,3,'article_img/20180410014216_34.jpg'),(46,'成为母亲后 她们问女人非要生孩子不可吗','2018-04-10 01:42:58.603148','2018-04-10 01:42:58.603173','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为人父母的人都承认生养孩子确实不易。但大多数人会觉得他们得到的回报让一切艰辛都是值得的。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然而，也有极少数的人真的后悔要了小孩。BBC为你讲述3位母亲的真实故事和感受。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43620632\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">父母吵架伤害的不止是感情 还有孩子的健康</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/uk-42104288\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">当我凝视儿子眼睛时 能看到那个强暴者影子</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">雷恰尔（Rachel</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">化名）的故事</strong></p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/13FB8/production/_100684818_capture.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/13FB8/production/_100684818_capture.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"雷恰尔\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">雷恰尔很多时候是单身母亲</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">雷恰尔今年50多岁，她有3个孩子，最小的17岁。她告诉BBC，如果时间能够倒流，她不会要小孩。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">雷恰尔很多时候是单身母亲， 因此一人养育3个孩子非常艰难。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">她说，有时候她觉得自己都还不够成熟，如何还要为另外一个小生命负责？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">她觉得带孩子就是无穷无尽的伺候他们的吃喝拉撒睡，一点也不好玩。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">雷恰尔承认她当时并没有认真想清楚，有了小孩会给她生活带来什么样的影响。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">她说，如果她意识到这一点，当初就不会要小孩了。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是，她说她这样说会感到内疚，因为她非常爱自己的孩子。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;你觉得你自己不是一位好妈妈。你会永远有这种内疚，永远也不会摆脱。你还会想孩子们是否知道呢。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;但是，生活不应该是你牺牲自己的生命、自由，就是为了他们能过得好。&quot;</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/38937178\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">晒母乳喂养照哪儿来的说三道四</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2016/11/161120_world_cambodia_surrogacy_arrest\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">澳洲女子在柬埔寨从事非法代孕业务被捕</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">能承认这一点很不容易，因为&quot;别人会觉得你这个人不怎么样&quot;。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">雷恰尔特别希望有同感的女性不要受到丑化。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;我感到非常孤立。我觉得自己有问题。但如果我能够坦诚地探讨这些问题，而且有人能够理解，也许会让我更容易尽好做母亲的职责。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">像雷恰尔这样想法的女性到底有多普遍很难得知，因为很少有人公开谈论类似的感受。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2016年，德国政府所做的调查发现，在1200名参加调查的人当中，8％的人后悔要小孩。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2015年，以色列社会学家Donath发表一份研究，里面讲述了那些后悔生小孩的女性的故事。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那些后悔要小孩的女性还坚称这与产后抑郁症是两回事。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">艾利森（</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Alison</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">，化名）</strong></p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/166C8/production/_100684819_f9eb6b3b-f67d-49bd-a438-77d44657c812.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/166C8/production/_100684819_f9eb6b3b-f67d-49bd-a438-77d44657c812.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"艾利森\" width=\"624\" height=\"351\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">艾利森说，她不知道如何逗儿子玩</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;我刚才看到幸福的一家人，他们的房子和花园。孩子上学去了，就像童话一样，&quot;她说。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">艾利森是被领养的。她成长的过程中总是梦想将来有一天也能有自己的家。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是，直到她生了第一个儿子后才发觉自己并不太母性。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">她特想走出家庭，回到工作岗位上以逃避为人之母的新角色。因此不到６个月她就回去上班了。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;我有时会请假，把孩子交给保姆，就是想给自己一天的空闲，&quot;她说。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-42046243\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">我为什么要捐献自己的卵子？</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/science-39341040\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">精子成功让卵子受孕的秘密是什么？</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;我不是不想跟儿子在一起，但我不知道该做什么。我对跟小孩玩游戏不在行。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为了不让儿子孤独，艾利森和丈夫又生了一个男孩。现在两个孩子都上了大学。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">她承认如果当初知道当母亲的责任，她就不会要小孩了。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">她解释说：&quot;如果别人幸福自己就感到幸福，这太不爽了。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;也许我的事业会更好。我15年送孩子上学，绝对限制了我事业的发展。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">艾利森强调她非常爱孩子，然而承认回过头来看自己太自私了，不适合要孩子。&quot;我嫌他们侵占了我的时间。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">她说，女性一般不愿意对此敞开心扉，因为担心别人会对此说三道四。她们也不愿意被认为太自私。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但问题是，如果你不想要小孩，那你就不是一个好母亲。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">乔伊（</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Joy，化名</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">）</strong></p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/0B20/production/_100684820_e705474b-4c89-42ec-8cab-1f89f6419cc2.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/0B20/production/_100684820_e705474b-4c89-42ec-8cab-1f89f6419cc2.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"乔伊\" width=\"624\" height=\"351\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">乔伊有个女儿</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">20年前乔伊生了个女儿，但其实她在更早时就意识到自己并不想当母亲。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;当大家谈论有人把孩子递到你手里，你浑身充满了无尽的爱。我丝毫没有这种感觉，只是觉得巨大的责任感，&quot; 乔伊说。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">回忆女儿小时候，乔伊似乎找不到什么喜悦的感觉，每天都如此艰辛，一天一天的熬过去。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;我猜可能每位母亲都经历过这种感觉。但我只能说我找不到彻底享受的时刻，非常不好过。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">乔伊认为她可能没有其他母亲所拥有的母性。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/uk-41970974\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中国妈妈坐月子上了BBC时事讨论节目</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-39544837\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">万米高空 靓空姐变身接生婆</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;我一直想知道是否别的母亲都没讲真话。她们把做母亲描述得如何美妙，而实际上有一天她们会坦白向我承认不是这样的，&quot;她说。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我似乎没能力做一位善良、热情与可爱的母亲。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">乔伊说，她希望回去上班，继续自己的事业。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">乔伊的女儿怀疑过母亲对她的爱。但乔伊坚持说自己绝对爱女儿，只不过两人之间的关系不是如胶似漆而已。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">乔伊说，如果更多的女性能够敞开心扉，也许对女性一定要成为母亲的压力会小一些。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;如果女性能够诚实地面对自己该有多好。如果生小孩，组建家庭对你来说非常重要，那么就全心全意地去做。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;但是，如果你强烈感觉&#39;自己对此无感觉&#39;，那么不要畏惧或是感到耻辱。你可以站出来，大声说&#39;我就是那个不想当妈妈的人，我不想要孩子&#39;。&quot;</p><p><br/></p>','为人父母的人都承认生养孩子确实不易。但大多数人会觉得他们得到的回报让一切艰辛都是值得的。\n\n然而，也有极少数','小说',0,3,'article_img/20180410014258_88.jpg'),(47,'记者来鸿：大英帝国怎么成了“万恶之源”','2018-04-10 01:44:08.841452','2018-04-10 01:44:08.841478','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从小到大，我听到的阴谋论不计其数，其中有些相当疯狂。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我听说，李小龙被妻子下毒，他知道后，亲自动手惩治她。我还听说，李小龙会飞，希特勒还活着，战争最后一刻，他乘坐吉普车逃脱盟军追捕，吉普车先是变成飞机，然后变成船、潜艇！希特勒偶尔还给世界发信号，宣称，&quot;我会回来的！&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是，有一个市井传言生命力特别旺盛：阿富汗所有的苦难，都是英国人造成的。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">小时候，我曾经想过，这是为什么呢？20几岁时我来到英国，后来我懂了，这种怀疑是有原因的。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-39229726\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">阿富汗与中国边界恐袭威胁 北京如何应对？</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-40615685\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">观点：中巴经济走廊为何引发争论？</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-40615678\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">IS&quot;革命圣地&quot;覆灭 &quot;热血青年&quot;何去何从？</a></p></li></ul><p><figure class=\"media-portrait has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/1036C/production/_100721466_0ff3255b-f94a-44f7-bfcf-bdc1d31a8e49.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1036C/production/_100721466_0ff3255b-f94a-44f7-bfcf-bdc1d31a8e49.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"BBC记者阿特拉菲\" width=\"976\" height=\"1204\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AULIYA ATRAFI</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">BBC波斯语记者阿特拉菲</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">几百年来，阿富汗一直是沙俄帝国和大英帝国之间的缓冲区。两个超级大国在这片&quot;三不管地带&quot;（no man&#39;s land，尤指战争期间两国交界处的无人地带）频繁有大动作。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据说，现代阿富汗版图划定的时候，阿富汗国王的看法根本无人理睬。1919年阿富汗独立之前，英国和阿富汗总过打过三次战争，之后英国人才永远离开。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">嗯？英国人真的永远离开了？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在阿富汗人心里，英国人仍然藏在阴影中，监视着他们，密谋、策划；英国人仍然能把阿富汗内政搞到一团糟。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有传说，英国间谍假扮阿訇，误导虔诚的信徒，还有英国间谍装作算命先生；我还听说过，祭台背后藏着财宝，四周的乞丐，其实都是保安。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">《记者来鸿》是BBC记者从世界各地发回的深度报道。希望它能成为您了解世界的一个窗口。更多阅读，</strong><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/fooc\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">请点击这里</a></p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/1CF4/production/_100721470_3f63e40a-6de3-4815-a320-282d69bd8f4d.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1CF4/production/_100721470_3f63e40a-6de3-4815-a320-282d69bd8f4d.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"历史上的英阿战争\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">MEPL</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">1880年，英国在迈万德（Maiwand）战役中落败</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">历史上的英阿战争：</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">英国曾经三次试图征服阿富汗，每一次都以失败告终。</em></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">第一次：沙皇俄国在阿富汗扩张势力令英国十分恼火。1839年英国入侵阿富汗，迅速占领喀布尔，扶持起傀儡政权。两年后，喀布尔民众起义。1841年冬英军被迫撤退，16000多官兵幸存者寥寥无几。</em></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">第二次：1878年英国再次入侵阿富汗，原因和结局几乎就是第一次的翻版。</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">这一次，</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">由于签署不平等条约</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">英国</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">还是</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">从阿富汗</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">攫取</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">了</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">大量利益。</em></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">第三次：1919年英阿</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">再次开战</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">。起因是阿富汗新一代军官决心废除与英国的不平等条约。这场战争后</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">英国被迫</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">承认阿富汗独立。</em></p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/12A7C/production/_100721467_de0a95f4-ec11-46a9-b878-56b339fd4cd0.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/12A7C/production/_100721467_de0a95f4-ec11-46a9-b878-56b339fd4cd0.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"BBC记者阿特拉菲\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AULIYA ATRAFI</span></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">痴迷阴谋论的并不是只有阿富汗人。一位库尔德朋友告诉我，如果下了一夜的雨，邻里有哪一堵墙倒塌了，妈妈都会埋怨英国人。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">伊朗有一部播放多年的肥皂剧，其中有个角色永远相信英国人在搞阴谋诡计，永远忧心忡忡。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我的朋友告诉我，在孟加拉，如果你显得很精明、很会算计的话，人们会说你像英国人。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在喀布尔，我们也有这样一个词，形容人血管里流着&quot;恶毒的英国血&quot;。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是，自从1980年代阿富汗爆发内战以来，我们心目中阴谋家的名单越来越长了，现在还包括巴基斯坦的情报部门、所谓的伊斯兰国，当然了，还有美国人。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">反反复复、一次又一次的外国干涉只会让阿富汗人的想象力越来越丰富。</strong></p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/4404/production/_100721471_ffe0d5b7-5daa-43f8-a970-23135f7df43f.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/4404/production/_100721471_ffe0d5b7-5daa-43f8-a970-23135f7df43f.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"1980年代在喀布尔的俄罗斯军队\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; fon