 inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">阿富汗</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">——</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&quot;帝国坟场&quot;</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">阿富汗位于欧亚大陆心腹</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">。</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">特殊的地理位置，使她成为历来的交通要冲、兵家必争之地。</em></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">从古至今，阿富汗</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">多次</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">经历大国入侵，但是她最后几乎总会把</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">对方</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">拖垮。因此人们总爱</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">把</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">阿富汗</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">称作“</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">帝国坟场</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">”。</em></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">除了历史上的大英帝国，</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">勃列日涅夫时期咄咄逼人的苏联</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">以及</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">冷战后信心爆棚的美国，</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">都曾</em><em style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">在阿富汗都曾陷入泥潭。</em></p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption body-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/16C07/production/_87719139_line976.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/16C07/production/_87719139_line976.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"Presentational grey line\" width=\"464\" height=\"2\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有一次在伦敦，一位阿富汗裔出租车司机向我抱怨说，外国人要偷走阿富汗的石油，藏在客机里偷偷运出来；还有人说，外国人的目光盯上了伊朗的铀。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在阿富汗，一名法官曾告诉我，本拉登是美国间谍，最后被干掉是因为他知道的太多了。还有人相信本拉登还活得好好的，在美国某个地方一个世外田园般的小岛上养尊处优呢。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">阿富汗的将军也会说，北约出钱、武器支持塔利班，他们甚至还说，敢于揭露这种内幕的翻译被从直升机上直接抛出去！</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还有传言说，北约部队从阿富汗走私犯手里购买毒品，藏在阵亡士兵的肚子里偷偷运回西方。据说，好多西方人从这个利润丰厚的行当中受益，其中包括英国王室。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/uk-42051922\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">留英&quot;海归&quot;第一人——清朝书生黄亚东</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/fooc/2015/02/150226_fooc_boring_imperialist\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">记者来鸿：&quot;大英帝国主义分子&quot;的自白</a></p></li></ul><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/1518C/production/_100721468_be337416-88f6-4379-bad1-664141436f5f.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/1518C/production/_100721468_be337416-88f6-4379-bad1-664141436f5f.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"BBC记者阿特拉菲\" width=\"976\" height=\"620\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AULIYA ATRAFI</span></span></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">去年我去见个朋友，他的父亲是位来自东部地区的部落首领。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">喝完绿茶，寒暄完毕，我一张嘴就意识到自己说错了话。我问他，你们那一片地区所谓的伊斯兰国怎么样了。首领口若悬河、滔滔不绝地给我上了一课，那种我已经听过无数次的言论。他自信满满地说，&quot;这都是伊斯兰国、美国人和英国人在玩儿游戏，付出代价的是阿富汗人！&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我略感不解，接着问道，&quot;但是，他们从中能得到什么好处呢?&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他坚持说，&quot;他们计划都是长线的，可能50年，他们以为我们都根本搞不懂。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;如果真这么简单，那他们也太愚蠢了。你知道吧，我们是能看到蛛丝马迹的，比如俄国、巴基斯坦和中国构建的新阵营。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;你好好想想，美国一星期就能摧毁塔利班政府，怎么就不能干掉几个藏在深山老林里的武装分子呢？&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">很明显，他以为自己赢了这场辩论，转过头，冲着麦加方向开始祷告。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/6B14/production/_100721472_7d09b375-f9cd-46d7-9afe-5638f4911370.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/6B14/production/_100721472_7d09b375-f9cd-46d7-9afe-5638f4911370.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"阿富汗\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">西方联军的干预并没有让阿富汗实现稳定</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最近在喀布尔，我刚刚和其它几个记者一起做完周五祷告，突然收到一条消息，显示有自杀炸弹攻击者在一座什叶派穆斯林的清真寺发起袭击。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我问，&quot;这是伊斯兰国干的吗？&quot;另外一名记者回答，&quot;还可能是犹太人或者基督徒干的。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我知道说什么也没用，但我还是接着问了一句，&quot;那能给他们带来什么好处呢？&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那位记者这次显得更加确信，他回答说，&quot;两方面，这类行动会在信徒和清真寺之间拉开距离，还会让穆斯林人分裂。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">绿区内的道路坑坑洼洼，刚离开清真寺，我们的裤腿还卷得高高的，胳膊下夹着祈祷用的小垫子，边走边聊。突然，我脑子里涌现出一个念头。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在这样一个语言、种族、信仰、思想造成严重分歧的国家，仍然能有一样东西让所有的阿富汗人齐心一致，那就是：</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">坚决</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">不信外国人。</strong></p><p><br/></p>','从小到大，我听到的阴谋论不计其数，其中有些相当疯狂。\n\n我听说，李小龙被妻子下毒，他知道后，亲自动手惩治她。','新闻',2,3,'article_img/20180410014408_89.jpg'),(48,'观点：中国对贸易战的态度为何如此强硬？','2018-04-10 01:45:29.798229','2018-04-10 01:45:29.798255','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国政府对美国发起此轮301调查的态度超级强硬，这出乎很多人的预料。此前，人们根据中国在类似事件中的反应特别是在有关领土争端中的表现，普遍预料，在特朗普政府的超强压力下，中国的应对模式还会像以前一样：嘴硬实软。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">美国这次可谓有备而来。三月下旬，美国宣布征收钢铝关税，对象包括其几个主要盟友，但随后又对一些盟友进行了“赦免”，中国没有赦免对象之中。对美国征收钢铝关税，中国官方反应一如之前人们预料的那样，表态比较有分寸，没有讲一些听起来具有挑衅性的过头话，在具体行动上，10多天后才出台反制措施。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这是贸易战第一回合的较量。由于之前美国通过舆论放出将对中国征收600亿美元商品的关税，而中国区区30亿美元的反制规模，这个数字对比一度让人误以为是对美国600亿关税的回应，从而在部分公众中引发了中国“未打先熊”的讥笑。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43553945\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美战略性贸易摩擦：断定贸易战到来为时尚早</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-43531738\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战：中国的余地和特朗普的目的</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43617332\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战打不起来？双方仍在积极谈判</a></p></li></ul><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/15FA9/production/_100752009_gettyimages-488725492.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/15FA9/production/_100752009_gettyimages-488725492.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"，\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">2015年北京国际航展上的波音777模型。中国是美国波音公司最大的市场之一。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">贸易战第二回合的较量。美国针对“中国制造2025”，公布了500亿美元商品的加征关税清单。这激怒了中国。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果说在第一回合中国官方的反应尚属克制，那么，当美方公布清单不久，中国就出台了对美国大豆、汽车和飞机的加征关税清单。外交部、商务部和驻美使馆这三大处在贸易战前线的机构同时表态，决心和美国打一场“同等规模、同等程度和同等力度”的贸易战，并“奉陪到底”。从此开始，人们发现中国的反应变了，不但报复措施出台迅速，而且态度较以往强硬。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43654210\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中国官媒单方面宣布中美贸易战“首战告捷”</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43651067\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美互亮底牌后 特朗普推特上继续放狠话</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43610276\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战阴影下的忧心者样本：美国红酒</a></p></li></ul><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/BC6B/production/_100753284_gettyimages-941707514.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/BC6B/production/_100753284_gettyimages-941707514.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"，\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">中国一家超市货架上的美国红酒。4月4日，中国宣布价值500亿美元的美国商品增税清单，红酒、大豆、波音飞机以及汽车在此之列。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当特朗普在中方出台报复措施后表示将对中国加征1000亿美元商品关税后，贸易战进入第三回合较量。中方三大机构表态不但要“奉陪到底”，而且“不惜一切代价”和美国打下去。事情到此，人们已不再怀疑，中国这次真要和美国打一场贸易战了。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在我看来，中方的态度称得上“超强硬”了。如何解释中国不惧应战的“超强”架势？原因有以下几个。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第一，中国官方认为自己已“退无可退”，再退下去，新一届政权不但在民众中会失去权威和“民望”，而且在国际上将会引起连锁反应，欧日可能“落井下石”，其他国家也会把中国当做“纸老虎”，从而在中美角逐的选边中纷纷选择美国，致使中国国际环境更加恶劣，崛起更加艰难。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在中国，不但官方，民间更是对美国“欺负”中国的行径耿耿于怀。过去中美实力差距太大，民众只能忍着，现在两国实力快速缩小，甚至如中国经济学家胡鞍钢所说，中国已全面超越美国。如果这次在美国的大棒下被迫签下“城下之盟”，那通过反腐好不容易建立起来的巨大权威在民众中就会迅速“流失”，这对依赖民粹和民族主义治理的新一届政权是不可承受之重。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在中国官民的认知中，美国不但以贸易逆差为由打击中国的高端制造业，阻扰中国经济转型，更由于同时在台湾和南海等问题上向中国发难，反映了特朗普政府要全面遏制中国崛起的态势。所谓“是可忍孰不可忍”，一旦在贸易战中形成了如此认知，要后退就非常困难，因为这不但关系“国运”，也直接关系到新政权自身的威信。何况，官方在贸易战的第二回合已经把话说“死”了，已经激发其民众的民族情绪，要后退已不可能，只能打下去。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43675458\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战酣之际南海刀光剑影风云激</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43299835\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">卡尔文森号历史性访越跟中国有什么关系</a></p></li></ul><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/E37B/production/_100753285_gettyimages-104549089.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/E37B/production/_100753285_gettyimages-104549089.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"中国计划向美国征收关税的产品中，包括大豆、小麦等\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">中国计划向美国征收关税的产品中，包括大豆、小麦等</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第二，吸取日本和朝鲜分别同美国打经济战和打拥核战的教训与经验，认识到两军相遇勇者胜，有敢打贸易战的决心和意志非常重要，用《环球时报》的话说，和美国打贸易战，打的是实力，也是意志。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">众所周知，在上世纪80年代，美国为在经济上遏制日本对自己的威胁，和日本打了一场经济战，迫使日本签署了“广场协议”，导致日元大幅升值，泡沫破裂，日本由此进入“失去的10年”。不管这“失去的10年”是否真由美日经济战导致，在中国官方和经济学者眼中，日本在经济战中的应对不力是一个坏榜样，常常被学者们拿来作为反面教材，提醒官方避免出现这种后果。与此相反，朝鲜则是一个好榜样，成功地顶住了国际社会主要是美国（和中国）的压力，发展出了核武器。尽管中国不喜欢朝鲜的核武器，并配合美国对朝鲜施压了最大压力，但是朝鲜在发展核武器上还是没有后退。特朗普虽然一度对朝鲜发出了战争威胁，但最后却不得不和朝鲜谈判。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">日朝这两个一反一正的案例让中国官方认识到，只有像朝鲜一样，有敢于同美国打一场“史诗级”贸易战的坚强意志，才能把美国逼退。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43595219\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">贸易战会不会将中国推向“失落的二十年”</a></p></li></ul><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/158AB/production/_100753288_gettyimages-941707700_1.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/158AB/production/_100753288_gettyimages-941707700_1.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"，\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">美国出口到中国的西洋参。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第三，中国官方或许认为自己也有资本和实力同美国打一场贸易战。同时，新一届政权认为，如果能够借贸易战的压力逼迫国内利益集团让步，推进深层次改革和开放，贸易战也未尝不可以打。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">单有意志还不够，也须有实力。日本在上世纪同美国的经济战之所以失败，应对失误只是一个方面，关键还在于实力不够，同美国有很大差距。日本当时的经济总量不到美国的40%，但日本国内却相信了经济膨胀的假象。一般来说，挑战国达到对象国80%的经济实力，基本可以和后者抗衡。中国去年的经济总量相当于美国的60%多，但多数看法认为，如果按照国内购买力计算，中国即使没有超过美国，也和美国差不多。所以中国隐藏了经济实力。假如在此基础上打个折扣，那么，中国的经济总量应该可以达到美国的80%左右。另外，中国还有日本当年不具备的庞大的国内市场。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然中美逆差很大，美国去年出口中国的商品1700多亿美元，中国出口美国的商品5800亿美元，看上去要打贸易战中国无疑将损失更大。但更重要的是，按照一些学者的说法，美国在计算两国贸易量时，并没有把美国企业在华直接出售产品包括在内，若把这部分价值计算在内，中美的贸易总量差别不大。所以，中国还有比关税更厉害的反击手段，即打击美国在华企业。此外，服务贸易也是选项之一。如果贸易战发展到极端，中国掌握的数万亿美元美国国债也是杀手锏。总之，在这些选项面前，中方会认为，不怕美国不退让。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">统计显示，中国的内需近年开始在经济发展中挑大梁，如果贸易战全面升级，官方可以加大政府投资力度，以应对短期困难，同时逼迫利益集团，开启多年不能推进的实质性的国内改革和开放，加快经济转型步伐，如果做到了这一步，在熬过最初几年的“苦日子”后，中国经济的内需基础更扎实，结构更健康。因此，从长期来看，官方也许会认为，打一场贸易战对中国并不是件坏事。</p><p><br/></p>','中国政府对美国发起此轮301调查的态度超级强硬，这出乎很多人的预料。此前，人们根据中国在类似事件中的反应特别','新闻',0,3,'article_img/20180410014529_64.jpg'),(49,'特朗普贸易政策下一步：脱离WTO规则','2018-04-10 01:46:46.122337','2018-04-10 01:46:46.122364','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">毫无疑问，各国负责贸易的官员现在正面临着一个大问题——那就是，特朗普的下一步棋会怎么走？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在第二次世界大战后的几十年里，美国可以说是贸易逐步自由化的最大推手。而现在，美国成了贸易自由化支持者们焦虑的主要原因。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在所谓经济民族主义的推动下，特朗普对待国际贸易的态度自信且富有对抗性。这也是本周不断升级的贸易紧张局势的主要因素。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有人担心他会破坏在过去四分之三个世纪里发展起来的全球贸易体系。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43651067\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美互亮底牌后 特朗普推特上继续放狠话</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-43531738\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战：中国的余地和特朗普的目的</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43595219\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">贸易战会不会将中国推向“失落的二十年”</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43610276\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战阴影下的忧心者样本：美国红酒</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">矛盾</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这是一个复杂的体系，在很大程度上基于通过世界贸易组织（WTO）来管理的规则，并辅之以一些国家间的贸易协定，以提供更深层次的合作。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">特朗普对这些促进深层次合作的协议没什么热情。他刚刚就职把美国从一个还未正式实施的协议中拉了出来——跨太平洋伙伴协议（TPP），并威胁退出另一个北美自由贸易协定。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/E392/production/_100685285_gettyimages-77756398.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/E392/production/_100685285_gettyimages-77756398.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"在中国重庆生产的摩托车\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">中国制造的摩托车是被美国关税打击的进口产品之一。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于世贸组织，特朗普政府则一直很矛盾。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最近美国的行动正是利用WTO规则作为借口。美国商务部在调查后决定对钢铁和铝加征关税，因为这些金属的进口对国家安全构成威胁。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这一结论的依据是美国军方需要来自本国的更可靠的供应来源。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">世贸组织的规则下，确实允许各国施加贸易壁垒，前提是为了保护国家安全，否则将不允许。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">国家安全是否真的是施加关税的理由？许多评论家，包括欧盟委员会和中国，都不相信这一点。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">关于进口洗衣机和太阳能电池板的关税是保障措施，这是为了应对进口激增而采取的行动，符合WTO规则。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">更难说的通的是美国还未实施的针对中国产品的关税措施，美国声称是因为中国盗用美国公司知识产权（如专利和设计）。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">WTO规则确实要求保护贸易成员的知识产权，除了美国，欧盟等国家或地区也对中国盗用知识产权担忧。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/E5FF/production/_100697885_aecaf2bc-0c05-47b2-b446-2da67a6582df.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/E5FF/production/_100697885_aecaf2bc-0c05-47b2-b446-2da67a6582df.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"关于北美贸易协定的一次记者会\" width=\"976\" height=\"350\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">美国威胁退出与加拿大和墨西哥签署的北美贸易协定。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是在大多数情况下，各国都应该根据WTO程序，由一个争议小组进行授权后，采取报复行为。美国上周才刚向WTO提出了正式申诉。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在WTO的任何裁决前要有几个月的时间，即使中国在裁决中输了，但如果不遵守裁决结果提出上诉，美国获得采取报复措施的授权就会进一步延迟。特朗普总统等得了这么久吗？</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">单边行动</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所以美国肯定可能抢跑，在WTO慢慢走程序时，决定动手。这很难与WTO的规则相符合。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">上周在世贸组织的一次会议上，中国官员警告说，美国的单边行动破坏了多边贸易体制，开了一个非常糟糕的先例。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国常驻世贸组织代表张向晨在会上表示，各成员国应该共同行动，“把这个野兽锁回WTO规则的笼子”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">尽管如此，美国开启了争端解决程序，这可以被看作是特朗普政府认为世贸组织依然有效的一个信号。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">值得注意的是，中国正在进行第一次没有世贸组织裁决的报复性反击，尽管在规则框架下能找到依据。不过所涉及的规则是否在此情况下适用，存在争议。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/73DB/production/_100695692_gettyimages-936601492.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/73DB/production/_100695692_gettyimages-936601492.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"前国务卿蒂勒森\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">美国前国务卿蒂勒森被解雇反映出政府内部对贸易问题的分歧。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过，特朗普政府确实与其前任在贸易方面的态度截然不同。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">激励着特朗普和其团队的经济民族主义，倾向于看到其他国家在开展不公平贸易，认为贸易赤字是软弱的表现，而贸易协定是有缺陷和不公平的。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">前首席战略家史蒂夫·班农是经济民族主义最有影响力的人物，特朗普确实解雇了他，但两人的分歧并不在贸易领域。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其他持有类似观点的官员还处于贸易决策的关键位置，美国商务部部长罗斯（WilburRoss），负责贸易谈判的美国贸易代表莱特希泽（Robert Lighthizer），和总统的贸易顾问、国家贸易委员会主任彼得·纳瓦罗（Peter Navarro）。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">班农的离职并没有反映出政府内对经济民族主义的分歧。但前国家经济委员会负责人加里·科恩的辞职反映出这点。科恩被视为抵制政府内经济民族主义的一员。国务卿蒂勒森（Rex Tillerson）的解雇也反映出他与总统的一些分歧，包括加征钢铁和铝关税。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">特朗普总统关于贸易的核心观点之一是，其他国家占了美国便宜。当然，美国的贸易壁垒是全球最低的。关税是适用于进口的税收，最容易衡量贸易壁垒的高低，这一指标上，美国的平均水平很低。但并非像纳瓦罗声称的，美国关税是世界上最低的。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">香港根本没有关税，取决于计算平均关税的方式，其他几个国家的平均关税低于美国。但是，美国关税确实相对较低。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/139DD/production/_100694308_gettyimages-866744652.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/139DD/production/_100694308_gettyimages-866744652.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"美国轻型卡车\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">美国贸易壁垒相对较低，但某些商品比如轻型卡车的关税较高</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有些商品在美国征收的关税很高，在贸易领域被称为“关税高峰”。一些农产品关税超过100％，轻型卡车则有25％的关税。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这是否意味着其他国家正在利用美国关税政策？这点有争议。贸易经济学家的主流观点是，收关税负面影响最主要体现在关税施加国的买家。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">主要受益者</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这些买家不得不支付更多费用，因为他们的供应商不得不提高价格弥补关税带来的损失，而且国内供应商因为得到关税的保护，也会提高自己的价格。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有时候，那些受影响的买家需要使用这些进口品进行生产，钢铁和铝材就是一例。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所以有很多贸易经济学家认为，美国低关税的主要受益者是美国本身，特别是美国消费者。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但特朗普总统重点放在生产者身上——企业和他们的雇员，他们认为自己受到低成本的打击，特别是来自中国的不公平竞争。</p><p><br/></p>','毫无疑问，各国负责贸易的官员现在正面临着一个大问题——那就是，特朗普的下一步棋会怎么走？\n\n在第二次世界大战','散文',0,3,'article_img/20180410014646_17.jpg'),(50,'中美贸易战打不起来？双方仍在积极谈判','2018-04-10 01:47:40.191200','2018-04-10 01:47:40.191228','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国宣布对美国包括猪肉和葡萄酒在内的128种进口产品加征最多25％关税，作为对美国3月初对中国钢铁和铝施加关税的报复性反击。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">周一起实施的关税预计将影响30亿美元（约合188亿人民币）进口商品。中国此前曾表示不想进行贸易战，但如果其经济受到损害就不会坐视不管。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">特朗普则坚持认为“贸易战是件好事”，而且美国应该“轻松”赢得胜利。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43536220\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美对垒：十问贸易战 输赢且慢论</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-43531738\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战：中国的余地和特朗普的目的</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">哪些产品受到影响？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">除现有进口关税外，美国的废铝和冷冻猪肉将被加征25％额外关税。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其他几种美国食品，包括坚果、新鲜水果、干果、人参和葡萄酒将被加征15％的关税。针对钢筋的关税同样会被加征15%。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这些产品中并未包含美国对中国出口的主要产品，包括大豆、波音飞机等。中国是美国大豆的最大买家，来自美国本土种植的三分之一大豆销往中国，出口额达到140亿美元；此外，波音也被认为是此次贸易战中的主要目标。2015年，中国与波音签下价值380亿美元的订单。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/96C3/production/_100659583_hi04578178afpgetty.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/96C3/production/_100659583_hi04578178afpgetty.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"波音公司生产的787型客机，在等待交付给中国南方航空公司。\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AFP/GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">波音公司生产的787型客机，在等待交付给中国南方航空公司。</span></figcaption></figure></p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">先放出狠话，再坐下谈话</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中共喉舌《人民日报》称，本次中国反击针对的是“232措施”，即美国在3月23日起对钢铁和铝加征关税的措施。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3月23日后，特朗普又签署了贸易备忘录，宣布基于美方“301调查”结果，将对中国价值600亿美元的商品加征关税。但按照美国方面的规定，签署备忘录后15日内才公布正式清单及关税，此后30天交由公众讨论，随后才会生效实施。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">复旦大学国际关系与公共事务学院学者马萧萧称，“备忘录相当于子弹上膛，但是真正扣动扳机的是45天后公布的正式清单。这就为双方的谈判与协商提供了余地”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">事实上，美国财政部长姆努钦（Steven Terner Mnuchin）和中国国务院副总理刘鹤也在密集接触，重启双边贸易谈判。谈判开始后不久，美国贸易代表莱特希泽（Robert Emmet Lighthizer）在接受媒体采访时表示，中美之间有希望通过谈判来避免此次关税大战，并且美国对华加征关税产品清单的公示天数将从30天延长至60天，也就是说，在今年6月之前，美国都不会对中国相关产品进行增收关税。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这些信息都表示双方在积极谈判，试图避免贸易战。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/7622/production/_100524203_34575.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/7622/production/_100524203_34575.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"美国犹他州詹森市的艾斯克兰迪农场正在收割燕麦。\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">CNS</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">美国犹他州詹森市的艾斯克兰迪农场正在收割燕麦。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">贸易战</strong><strong style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">打不起来？</strong></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">马萧萧向BBC中文介绍，上世纪美国曾多次对日本发起“301调查”，几乎都是以双方在最终清单公布前达成妥协而告终。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“首先，现在贸易战还未真正开打，我更愿意称其为美国单边的贸易保护主义行为。我认为中国正在小心避免贸易战，因为中国依然想进入美国市场和进行对外投资。”香港科技大学商学院经济发展研究中心主任黎麟祥教授说。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">黎麟祥表示，中美贸易战即使真正爆发，也不会持久，涉及范围也不会很广，因为中美还有很多领域需要合作，比如朝核问题。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">世贸组织总干事阿泽维多向BBC表示，“没有人认为这（贸易战）是小事情，即使美国政府也是如此。所以现在双方在进行沟通，因为人们意识到这件事的严肃程度，以及它对全球经济的影响。”</p><p><br/></p>','中国宣布对美国包括猪肉和葡萄酒在内的128种进口产品加征最多25％关税，作为对美国3月初对中国钢铁和铝施加关','散文',0,3,'article_img/20180410014740_5.jpg'),(51,'中美贸易战阴影下的忧心者样本：美国红酒','2018-04-10 01:48:58.973315','2018-04-10 01:48:58.973340','<p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在美国旧金山以东大约一个小时车程的加利福尼亚州利弗莫尔谷（Livermore Valley），大约5000箱威迪酒庄的葡萄酒正在仓库中等待被运往中国，但被突然叫停。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这些酒卷入了一场更大的贸易争端：美国和中国已经互相威胁，要对包括美国葡萄酒在内的价值数十亿美元的产品征收关税。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在这场贸易战中，葡萄酒像个棋子，更大的图景涉及到美国对当前中美贸易部分规则的不满，具体涉及中国政府补贴和迫使美国科技公司和汽车制造商交出知识产权。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当两国开始坐下来谈判的时候，像葡萄酒这样的行业让人们得以窥探这场对抗中的风险。这种风险已经导致了金融市场的动荡，并引发了贸易战的警告。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;这有点等着看戏的感觉。&quot;威迪家族产业国际销售副总裁迈克尔·帕尔（Michael Parr）说，该公司将中国列为十大市场之一，并在关税谈判爆发时暂停发货。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">美国官员淡化了中国报复美国经济的危险。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43595219\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战会将中国推向&quot;失落的二十年&quot;？</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43579779\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">世贸组织总干事阿泽维多谈中美贸易战：后果严重</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43553945\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美战略性贸易摩擦：断定贸易战到来为时尚早</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国将葡萄酒列入价值30亿美元的128种潜在关税目标产品名单。中国认为，自己迅速增长的中产人数和由此带来的巨大市场，足以令美国保持谨慎。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">即使对于两国之间贸易占比很小的葡萄酒，这也是毋庸置疑的。出口仅占美国葡萄酒总销售额的5％。其中仅有约5％、出口额约为7900万美元的葡萄酒到达中国市场。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但无论如何，酿酒商都担心关税。他们表示，即使他们现在有能力负担中国市场的损失，中国对该行业的未来也至关重要。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;我们不能失去市场份额，&quot;帕尔说。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/14366/production/_100609728_gettyimages-655831176.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/14366/production/_100609728_gettyimages-655831176.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"Chinese students taste and study wine during a class on March 16, 2017 at the School of Wine of the Dijon Business School.\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AFP/GETTY</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">自2000年，中国的红酒消费量增长近五倍，进口量从1％上升至33%左右。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当帕尔于1994年在中国开拓市场时，为中国的第一家外国葡萄酒进口商工作。那里大部分产品针对的是外国人和外国商人。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但中国人的口味已经改变了。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">英国葡萄酒研究机构Wine Intelligence研究总监周川说，2000年以来，中国的红酒消费量增长近五倍，进口量占消费总量的比例从1％上升至33%左右。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对葡萄酒的兴趣也有助于推动旅游业—— 2016年，中国游客成为了纳帕谷最多的外国游客群。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国是纳帕谷葡萄酒列车（Napa Valley Wine Train）第三大国际市场；在加利福尼亚的贝林格和斯特林葡萄园，20%的买家说普通话。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">威迪（Wente）是一个家族葡萄园，每年生产约70万箱葡萄酒，出口约占五分之一。受益于需求的激增，今年对中国的出口在关税谈判之前上涨了80％。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;在增长率和增长潜力方面，中国是最重要的市场之一，&quot;帕尔说。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/F546/production/_100609726_wente.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/F546/production/_100609726_wente.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"Michael Parr at a wine event in Fuzhou China in February 2017\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">BBC C/O MICHAEL PARR</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">迈克尔·帕尔表示，在中国的葡萄酒市场，美国不能落后于其它国家。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在法国葡萄酒一直占据的主导地位的中国市场，美国葡萄酒正在奋起直追。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">美国瓶装酒占中国进口葡萄酒比例不到5％，部分原因是由于中国的高关税。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">澳大利亚和智利近年来与中国签署了自由贸易协定以减少这些税收，这帮助了他们的销售。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在2013年奥巴马总统为习近平举办的晚宴上，山脊酒庄（Ridge Vineyards）的一款酒成为晚宴用酒，随后在中国的销量飙升。山脊酒庄表示，拟议的15％关税将进一步提高价格，使美国公司处于不利位置。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这家酒庄的主席大卫·阿马迪亚（David Amadia）说， &quot;我们在某种程度上已经在做艰苦的搏斗了，现在如果再增加15％......我认为会对业务有影响。&quot;</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">加州葡萄酒研究所（The California Wine Institute）代表着美国约1,000个葡萄园和酒庄的利益，它一直在中国的社交媒体上做宣传活动，通过举办品酒大师班等方式提高加州葡萄酒的形象。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">该组织认为，白宫应该支持葡萄酒出口。新的15％的税率可能会对进军中国市场造成&quot;灾难性&quot;影响。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">该研究所的国际营销副总监林赛·加拉格尔 (Linsey Gallagher)说，&quot;另加的15％关税可能会让我们失望。&quot;</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/A17D/production/_100614314_gettyimages-459325068.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/A17D/production/_100614314_gettyimages-459325068.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"Chinese President Xi Jinping\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">POOL</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">中美双方互相威胁贸易反制，但有人希望本次贸易战以相互妥协告终。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">尽管担忧未来，分析师预计短期内的经济损失将有限。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在中国内部，关税可能意味着更高的价格。但在中国葡萄墙（Grape Wall of China）博客上撰文的北京葡萄酒顾问吉姆·博伊斯（Jim Boyce）说，美国品牌很可能能够吸引许多已经准备花更多钱的顾客。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&quot;当然，没有关税是最好的。但其影响并不像一些人想得那么糟，&quot;他说。</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-43531738\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战：中国的余地和特朗普的目的</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43536220\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美对垒：十问贸易战 输赢且慢论</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果中国的需求确实下滑，许多酿酒商表示他们有信心在其他市场找到买家。但数量很小，不希望价格有变化。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/4C55/production/_100614591_gettyimages-671691800.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/4C55/production/_100614591_gettyimages-671691800.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"Vineyards in the Malibu region of California on April 19, 2017.\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">AFP/GETTY</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">大多数的美国红酒都是内销。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果经济损害有限，那威胁的意义又是什么？</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">彼得森国际经济研究所的高级访问研究员加里·胡夫鲍尔（Gary Hufbauer）说，关税的威胁在提醒美国，中国打算进行报复，并且会在飞机等大型项目上保持选择权。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但他表示，中国的拟征关税的清单里充满了葡萄酒等高端产品，这都不是为经济，而是为制造政治痛苦，创造妥协条件。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中美贸易战阴影下的葡萄酒业和其他许多行业，都期待这场贸易战能有好结果。</p><p><br/></p>','在美国旧金山以东大约一个小时车程的加利福尼亚州利弗莫尔谷（Livermore Valley），大约5000箱','小说',0,3,'article_img/20180410014858_30.jpg'),(52,'中美贸易战会将中国推向“失落的二十年”？','2018-04-10 01:49:47.502706','2018-04-10 01:49:47.502732','<p class=\"story-body__introduction\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">特朗普宣布对600亿美元中国商品征税，仅7个小时后，中国针锋相对公布反制措施，中美贸易战序幕拉开，WTO总干事称，全球经济增长可能因此迅速下滑。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“贸易战”对于中国而言还比较新鲜，但美国则驾轻就熟，在过去百年对多国发动过，其中频度最高就是中国近邻日本，对日贸易战在上世纪80年代达到高潮。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当前中国和当时日本的境遇惊人地相似。日本在与美国贸易战后进入“失落的二十年”，经济增长放缓，崛起的势头最终彻底瓦解。中国是否会重蹈日本的覆辙？</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-43553945\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美战略性贸易摩擦：断定贸易战到来为时尚早</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-43531738\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美贸易战：中国的余地和特朗普的目的</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-43536220\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">中美对垒：十问贸易战 输赢且慢论</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中国和日本面临哪些相似境遇？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“1980年代日本工业产能开始逐步超过美国，这使美国人感到害怕。相似的是，目前中国强劲的制造业竞争力也被看作是导致美国工作机会减少的主因。”香港科技大学商学院经济发展研究中心主任黎麟祥教授认为，在面临被超越的时候，美国无法接受超大贸易逆差。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">上世纪80年代初，当时日本对美国的贸易顺差达到370亿美元，并占据了美国对外贸易逆差的主要部分。因此，美国传统的中西部和东北部等工业中心失业率走高，甚至翻倍，最终形成“铁锈地带”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“当前中美之间则达3750亿美元。即使算上通胀因素，中美间顺差占比也高于当年。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">黎麟祥指出，值得注意的是很多中国企业属于国有，获得了政府的各种帮助；当年的很多日本企业也在各自财团内部的银行获得便宜的信贷。美国认为这些对企业的补贴造成不公平竞争。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape has-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); clear: both; white-space: normal;\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/4D49/production/_100558791_gettyimages-936577972.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/4D49/production/_100558791_gettyimages-936577972.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"特朗普\" width=\"976\" height=\"800\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(189, 189, 189); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span><figcaption class=\"media-caption\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">Image caption</span><span class=\"media-caption__text\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.33333; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\">特朗普称将对价值600亿美元的中国商品加征关税。但目前具体清单还未公布。</span></figcaption></figure></p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“所以美国认为必须要对此采取行动。”受这些因素促使，美国从1975年开始，共针对日本发起了15次“301调查”，甚至一度被称为“上世纪80年代的珍珠港事件”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">相似的原因，促使美国时隔40年后再次举起贸易战的“大棒”。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">香港中文大学商学院会计学院高级讲师李兆波称，除了中日对美贸易顺差外，80年代日本和当前中国的GDP都排在世界第二，两次贸易战可以看作贸易逆差一方的报复。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">站在美国的角度，中日的贸易角色何其相似。反观国内，中国和80年代的日本也有几乎差不多的情况——人口增长趋缓，处于老龄化社会前夕；多年房地产价格高居不下，泡沫开始出现等等。</p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中日有哪些不同？</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然两场贸易战背景相似，但在一些关键领域也有较大区别。在经济学家看来，这些区别使美国对中国发动贸易战的意愿更强。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">首先是经济体量的不同。黎麟祥称，中国占美国GDP的百分比，要大于80年代的日本，中国增速也更快，使其很可能在2030年经济上超过美国。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">相比当年的日本，美国对中国不满之处也更多，除了贸易不平衡外，还有知识产权盗窃等问题。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">更重要的是，黎麟祥看来，日本当时对美国在政治和军事上更依赖。中国则比较独立于美国。日本被看作美国的盟友，中国则被看做战略竞争对手。所以在美国眼中，中国的今日带来的威胁要远大于当年的日本。“美国对待当前的问题会更严肃。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">李兆波则提到，80年代日本在家电等行业已经因产品质量赢得良好声誉，很多日本的全球化品牌产生在这个时期，就全球化品牌数量而言，今日的中国不及当时的日本，而且日本产品主要在本土生产，中国则主要进行代工。</p><p><figure class=\"media-landscape no-caption full-width\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; margin: 24px -24.6406px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"image-and-copyright-container\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; position: relative;\"><img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/181E1/production/_100558789_gettyimages-871865938.jpg\" datasrc=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/181E1/production/_100558789_gettyimages-871865938.jpg\" class=\"responsive-image__img js-image-replace\" alt=\"getty\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" data-highest-encountered-width=\"624\" style=\"border: 0px; color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; max-width: 100%; user-select: none; width: 616.203px; transition: opacity 0.2s ease-in; display: block;\"/><span class=\"off-screen\" style=\"color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px); overflow: hidden; border: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; position: absolute !important; height: 1px !important; width: 1px !important;\">图片版权</span><span class=\"story-image-copyright\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.25px; line-height: 1.14286; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 8px 1px; vertical-align: baseline; text-transform: uppercase; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); bottom: 0px; position: absolute; right: 0px;\">GETTY IMAGES</span></span></figure></p><h2 class=\"story-body__crosshead\" style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(30, 30, 30); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; margin: 32px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">日元突然升值的后果</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">日本经济持续衰退，进入“失落的二十年”，并非贸易战直接导致的。“本质上是日本未能成功处理与美贸易摩擦的结果。”中国复旦大学国际关系与公共事务学院学者马萧萧表示。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">80年代对日的贸易战并未帮助美国显著减少贸易逆差，美国又将原因归结为美元对日元汇率的高估。1985年，在美国的主导下，美、日等五国在纽约广场饭店举行会议，签署广场协议（The Plaza Accord），五国政府联合干预外汇市场，诱导美元对主要货币的汇率有秩序地贬值，以解决美国巨额贸易赤字问题。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">广场协议后，日元升值导致贸易顺差减少。为了应对日元升值带来的出口压力，以及美国不断发起的贸易战，日本积极提振内需，日本采取了宽松的货币政策和积极的财政政策，最终造成疯狂的地产泡沫。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">马萧萧称，“日元急剧升值，导致了日本实体经济外流、资本涌入等一系列问题，造成了资产泡沫，最后导致了崩溃。”</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">黎麟祥对此也表示同意。“但我不认为中国会同意签署任何与广场协议相似的协议，中国更独立于美国，日本则更依赖于美国。中国会对美国这类需求进行抗争，而日本却没能力这么做。”</p><ul class=\"story-body__unordered-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-41840897\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">观点：奋发有为Vs保守孤立——中美关系会进入对抗期吗</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-41827714\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">观察：特朗普对华贸易调查中的几大难题</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-41013152\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">再谈修昔底德陷阱：中美较量 必有一战？</a></p></li><li class=\"story-body__\" style=\"\"><p><a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/business-40971778\" class=\"story-body__link\" style=\"border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: inherit; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(17, 103, 168, 0.3);\">时隔七年重启 特朗普版中美贸易战指向何处</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">日美、中美贸易战本质上的不同在于中国比日本更具自主性。马萧萧认为，中国应对摩擦的步伐是自主的，调整范围可控。黎麟祥认为，中国应从日本身上学到，在金融领域的改革和汇率改革上，应该坚持自己的路径，而不要屈服于外国的要求。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">李兆波认为，日本政府当时犯了很多错误，首相更换得过于频繁再加上人口老龄化，使问题加剧，中国也有老龄化问题，但领导人比较稳定。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最终的结果，中美贸易战可能会“大而化小”。黎麟祥表示，中美贸易战即使真正爆发，也不会持久，涉及范围也不会很广。中国和美国还有很多领域需要合作，比如朝核问题。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">至于是否会进入“失落的二十年”，李兆波认为不太可能，人民币和股票市场还未完全开放，政府可以有效控制，而且中国和众多发展中国家关系良好。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">马萧萧称，整体来看，中国经济正在逐步向消费导向转变，贸易战的结果中国能够承受。本次贸易摩擦的背后是中美核心竞争力之争，以目前中国的体量以及应对措施来看，贸易战将中国推入一个失去的多少年，应该不会出现。</p><p><br/></p>','特朗普宣布对600亿美元中国商品征税，仅7个小时后，中国针锋相对公布反制措施，中美贸易战序幕拉开，WTO总干','小说',0,3,'article_img/20180410014947_99.jpg');
